hadiths[271]{hadithnumber,text}:
4701,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima-bin-qa'nab aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne Mughira hazaami se aur Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Amr Naqid ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena se ( Mughira aur Sufiyan ( donon ne abu-Zinad se unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur Zuhair ki hadis mein hai, unhon (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) ne hadis ki nisbat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchai (aap se bayan ki) aur Amr ne kaha : (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : log us aham mamley ( hukumat ( mein Quraish ke taabea (matahat) hain, musalman , qureshi musalmanon ke peechhey chalney waley hain aur kaafir , qureshi kaafiron ke peechhey chalney waley hain."
4702,"Hammam-bin-Munabbah se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hai jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kiya, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik hadis ye thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : log us mamley ( khilafat ya hukumat ( mein Quraish ke taabe (matehat) hain, musalman , qureshi musalmanon ke taabe hain aur kaafir , qureshi kaafiron ke peechhey chalney waley hain."
4703,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : achai aur burai ( donon ( mein log Quraish ki pairwi kartey hain.
4704,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tak (un ( logon mein do insan bhi baqi raheingey , hukumat ka muamla Quraish mein hoga."
4705,"Husain (bin-Abdur-Rehman ( ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke main apne walid (Hazrat Samra-bin-junaada (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : is baat ka khaatma us waqt tak na hoga jab tak usmein baara(12) ja-nashin na guzrein . phir aap ne koi baat ki jo mujh par waazeh na hui. maine apne walid se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya hai? unhon-ne kaha : aap ne farmaya hai : wo sab Quraish mein se hongey."
4706,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : logon ki imaarat jari rahegi yahan tak ke baara(12) ashkhaas unke wali banengey . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi baat kahi jo mujh par waazeh na hui, maine apne walid se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaayaa? unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo sab Quraish mein se hongey."
4707,"abu-Awana ne Samak se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki, lekin unhon-ne ye bayan nahi kiya : logon ki imaarat ka silsila chalta rahega."
4708,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Samak se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baara khaleefaon (ke ahad ( tak Islam ghalib rahega. phir aap ne aik kalima farmaya jis ko main nahi samajh saka , maine apne walid se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaayaa? unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo sab Quraish mein se hongey."
4709,"Dawud ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baara khulafaa (ke ahad ( tak Islam ka ghalba jari rahega. phir aap ne koi baat kahi jis ko main nahi samajh saka , maine apne walid se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya? unhon-ne kaha : aap ne farmaya : wo sab Quraish mein se hongey."
4710,"Abdullah-bin-Aun ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gaya, mere sath mere walid they, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : baara khulafaa (ke ahad ( tak musalsal ye Deen ghalib aur) dushmanon se) mehfooz rahega. phir aap ne koi kalima farmaya jisey logon ne mujhey sunney na diya, maine apne walid se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya? unhon-ne kaha : aap ne farmaya : wo sab Quraish mein se hongey."
4711,"Hatim-bin-Ismail ne muhajir-bin-mismaar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se riwayat ki, kaha : maine apne ghulam Naafe ke hath Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas khat bheja ke aap mujhey koi aisi hadis likh bhejen jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho. unhon-ne mujhey likh bheja ke us Juma ke din jiski Sham ko Hazrat ( Maaiz ( Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ko rajm (sangsaar) kiya gaya tha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : qiyamat tak ye Deen qaaim rahega , ya jab tak musalmanon par baara (12) khulafaa hukumat karengey jo sab ke sab Quraish mein se hongey aur maine aapko ye farmatey huey suna : musalmanon ki aik chhoti si jamat Kisraa ya aale Kisraa ka safaid mahal fateh karegi aur maine aapko ye farmatey huey suna : qiyamat ke qareeb kuchh kazzaab (jhunte) zahir hongey unse bachna. aur maine aapko ye farmatey huey suna : jab Allah Taala tum mein se kisi ko koi achi cheez de to wo apne aur apne ghar walon se shuruat kare. aur maine aapko ye farmatey suna : main hauz par tumhara pesh-rau hunga ."
4712,"ibne-abi-Ze'ib ne muhajir-bin-mismaar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne ibne-Samra-adwi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas paigham bheja ke aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jo hadis suni, wo hamein bayan kijiye . unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna. padhi. phir Hatim ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
4713,"Hisham ke walid (Urwa) ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab mere walid (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) zakhmi huey to main unke paas maujood tha. logon ne unki tareef ki aur kaha : Allah aapko achi jazaa de ! unhon (Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main (eik hi waqt mein) raghbat rakhney wala aur darney wala hun. logon ne kaha : aap kisi ko apna (jaa-nashin) bana dijiye. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main zindagi mein bhi tumharey maamlaat ka bojh uthaaoon aur marney ke baad bhi ? mujhey sirf ye khahish hai ke (qiyamat ke roz ( is khilafat se mere hissey mein ye aa jaey ke) hisab kitab ( barabar-sarabar ho jaey. na mere khilaf ho, na mere haq mein) chahey inaam na miley, magar saza se bach jaun ( agar main ja-nashin muqarrar karun to unhon-ne muqarrar kiya jo mujh se behtar they, yani Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) aur agar main tumhen aisey hi chhod dun to unhon-ne tumhen (jaa-nashin muqarrar kiye baghair) chhod diya jo mujh se ( bahut zyada ( behtar they. yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam). Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kiya to maine jaan liya ke wo ja-nashin muqarrar nahi karengey."
4714,"Salim ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kiya, kaha : main Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya. unhon-ne kaha : kya tum ko ilm hai ke tumharey walid kisi ko) apna ( ja-nashin muqarrar nahi kar rahe? maine kaha : wo aisa nahi karengey. wo kehney lagin : wo yahi karne waley hain. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine qism khaai ke main is mamley mein unse baat karunga, phir main khamosh ho gaya yahan tak ke subah ho gaee aur maine unse is mamley mein baat nahi ki thi, aur mujhey aisa lagta tha jaisey maine apne daain hath mein pahaad uthaya hua hai) mujh par apni qism ka bahut zyada bojh tha). aakhir kaar main wapas aaya aur unke paas gaya. unhon-ne mujh se logon ka haal malum kiya. main aapko halaat se ba-khabar karne laga, phir maine unse kaha : maine logon se aik baat suni thi aur wo sun kar maine qism khaai ke wo main aap se zaroor bayan karunga . logon ka khayal hai ke aap kisi ko apna ja-nashin nahi banaaein gey aur baat ye hai ke agar aap ka koi oonton ya bakriyon ka charwaha ho aur wo aap ke paas chala aaey aur unko aisey hi chhod de to aap yahi kahengey ki usne unko zaaya kar diya hai. so logon ki nigahbaani to us se zyada zaroori hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko meri raey theek malum hui, unhon-ne ghadi bhar sar jhukaaey rakha , phir meri taraf sar utha kar farmaya : bila shubah izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah apne Deen ki hifazat farmaeyga aur agar main kisi ko ja-nashin na banaun to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi ko ja-nashin muqarrar nahi kiya tha. aur agar main kisi ko ja-nashin banaun to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ja-nashin banaya tha? ( donon mein se kisi bhi misal par amal kiya ja sakta hai.) unhon (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kiya to maine jaan liya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tareeqey se kabhi nahi hatein gey aur wo kisi ko ja-nashin banaaney waley nahi."
4715,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne kaha : hamein Hasan Basri ne aur unhein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : Abdur-Rehman ! imaarat talab na karna kyonke agar tum ko talab karne se ( imaarat ( mili to tum uske hawale kar diye jaogey ( uski tamam tar zimma dariyaan khud uthao gey , Allah ki madad shamil na hogi) aur agar tumhen maangey baghair mili to ( Allah ki taraf se) tumhari madad hogi."
4716,"yoonus-bin-ubaid , Mansoor , Humaid aur Hisham-bin-Hassan sab ne Hasan Basri se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Jarir ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4717,"bareed-bin-Abdullah se riwayat hai, unhon-ne abu-Barda se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa ( Ash-ari ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aur mere chacha ke beton mein se do aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, un donon mein se aik ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! Allah Taala ne aap ki tauliyat mein jo diya uske kisi hissey par hamein ameer bana dijiye. doosrey ne bhi yahi kaha, aap ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! ham kisi aisey shakhs ko us kaam ki zimme-dari nahi detey jo usko talab karey, na aisey shakhs ko banatey hain jo uska khahish mand ho."
4718,"Humaid-bin-Hilal ne kaha : mujhey abu-Barda ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main banu-ash'ar mein se do aadmiyon ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aik meri daain taraf tha aur doosra meri baain taraf. un donon ne kisi mansab (ohdey) ka sawal kiya, us waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) miswak kar rahe they, aap ne farmaya : abu-Musa ! ya farmaya : Abdullah-bin-Qais ! tum kiya kehtey ho? maine kaha is zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kiya hai ! un donon ne mujhey ye nahi bataya tha ke unke dil mein kiya hai? aur na mujhey ye pata tha ke ye donon mansab ka sawal karengey. Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aisa lagta hai ke main ( aaj bhi) aap ke hont ke nichey miswak dekh raha hun jabke aap ka hont uper ko simtaa hua tha. aap ne farmaya : jo shakhs khahish mand hoga ham usey apne kisi kaam ki zimme-dari nahi ya ( farmaya : ( hargiz nahi dengey lekin abu-Musa ! ya farmaya : Abdullah-bin-Qais ! tum (zimme-dari sanbhaalney ke liye) chaley jao . to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Yaman bhej diya. phir ( sath hi ( unke peechhey Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhej diya, jab Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas pahunchey to Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tashrif laaiye aur unke baithney ke liye aik gaddaa bichhaya, to wahan us waqt aik shakhs rassiyon se bandhaa hua tha, unhon (Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu)) ne puchha : ye kon hai? (Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aik Yahudi tha, phir ye musalman ho gaya aur ab phir apne Deen (burai ke deen) par lot gaya hai aur Yahudi ho gaya hai. Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main us waqt tak nahi baithoon ga jab tak usko qatl na kar diya jaey, yahi Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka faisla hai. Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : haan , ( ham usko qatl kartey hain) aap baithiye , Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main us waqt tak nahi baithoon ga jab tak us shakhs ko qatl nahi kar diya jata jo Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka faisla hai, teen ( martaba yahi mukaalma (baat-cheet) hua) Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya, us shakhs ko qatl kar diya gaya, phir un donon ne aapas mein raat ke qiyam ke barey mein guftgu ki. donon mein se aik (yani (Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jahan tak mera mamla hai, main sota bhi hun aur qiyam bhi karta hun aur main apne qiyam mein jis ajr ki ummeed rakhta hun apni neend mein bhi usi ( ajr ( ki tawaqqo rakhta hun."
4719,"ibne-Hujaira akbar ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! kya aap mujhey aamil nahi banaaengey? aap ne mere kandhey par hath mar kar farmaya : Abu-Zar! tum kamzor ho, aur ye (amaarat) amanat hai aur qiyamat ke din ye sharmindagi aur ruswai ka baais hogi, magar wo shakhs jisne usey haq ke mutabiq qabool kya aur is mein jo zimme-dari is par Aaiz hui thi usey (achi tarah) ada kya. (wo sharmindagi aur ruswai se mustashna hoga.)"
4720,"abu Salim jeeshaani ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abu-Zar ! main dekhta hun ke tum kamzor ho aur main tumharey liye wahi cheez pasand karta hun jisey apne liye pasand karta hun, tum kabhi 2 aadmiyon par ameer na banna aur na yateem ke maal ke mutwalli banna."
4721,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-Numair teenon ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Amr bin Aus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, ibne-Numair aur Abu-Bakar ne kaha : unhon-ne is hadis ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya, Zuhair ki hadis mein hai) Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : adl karne waley Allah ke yahan Rehman azz-w-jall ki daain taraf noor ke membaron par hongey aur uske donon hath daaein hain, ye wahi log hongey jo apne faislon, apne ahal w ayaal aur jinke ye zimme daar hain unke mamley mein adl kartey hain."
4722,"ibne- Wahab ne kaha : mujhey Hurmala ne Abdur-Rehman bin shamasa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas kisi masley ke barey mein poochhney ke liye gaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : tum kin logon mein se ho? maine kaha : main Misr walon mein se hun. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : tumhara Hakim haaliya jang ke doran main tumharey sath kaisa raha? maine kaha : hamein uski koi baat buri nahi lagi, agar ham mein se kisi shakhs ka oont mar jata to wo usko oont de deta, aur agar ghulam mar jata to wo usko ghulam de deta aur agar kisi ko kharch ki zarurat hoti to wo usko kharch deta. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : mere bhai Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ke mamley mein us ne jo kuchh kya wo mujhey us se nahi rok sakta ke main tumhen wo baat sunaun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne is ghar mein kehtey huey suni, ( farmaya : (aey Allah ! jo shakhs bhi meri ummat ke kisi mamley ka zimme daar baney aur un par sakhti karey, to is par sakhti farma, aur jo shakhs meri ummat ke kisi mamley ka zimmedaar bana aur unke sath narmi ki, to uske sath narmi farma."
4723,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne Hurmala misri se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Shimasa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4724,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : sun rakho ! tum mein se har shakhs Hakim hai aur har shakhs se uski riaya ke mutaalliq sawal kya jaeyga, so jo ameer logon par muqarrar hai wo raai (logon ki bahbood ka zimmedaar) hai us se uski riaya ke mutaalliq puchha jaeyga aur mard apne ahale-khaana par raai (zimmedar) hai, us se uski riaya (zemmedari) ke mutaalliq sawal hoga aur aurat apne shauhar ke ghar aur uske bachchon ki raai hai, us se unke mutaalliq sawal hoga aur ghulam apne Malik ke maal mein raai hai, us se iske mutaalliq sawal kya jaeyga, sun rakho! tum mein se har shakhs raai hai aur har shakhs se uski riaya ke mutaalliq puchha jaeyga."
4725,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar, Ayub, Suhak bin Usman aur Usama (bin Zaid Lesi ( sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah Leis ne Naafe se bayan ki."
4726,"Ubaidullah (bin Umar-bin Hafs ( ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah Leis ne Naafe se bayan ki."
4727,"Ismail bin Jafar ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Naafe ki hadis ki tarah .) Yunus ne) Zohri ki hadis mein ye izafa kya : kaha : main samajhta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aadmi apne bap ke maal ka raai (zemmedar) hai aur us se uski riaya (zimmedari) ke mutaalliq sawal kya jaeyga"
4728,"Basar-bin-Saeed ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske ham-mana hadis riwayat ki hai."
4729,"abu-Ash'hab ne Hazrat Hasan Basri se riwayat ki ke Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad Hazrat Maaqil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas us marz mein unki iyaadat karne ke liye gaey jis mein unki wafat hui. Hazrat Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main tum ko aik aisi hadis sunata hun jis ko maine khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, agar mujhey (pakka) ilm hota ke main abhi aur zinda rahunga to main tumhen ye hadis na sunata, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : koi shakhs jis ko Allah Taala ne kisi bhi raiyat ka zimmedaar banaya wo jis din marey us haal mein marey ke wo apni riaya ke sath khayanat karne wala hai to Allah Taala is par jannat haram kar dega."
4730,"Yunus ne Hazrat Hasan Basri se riwayat ki, kaha : ibne- Ziyad Hazrat Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya wo us waqt ( bimar they aur) dard mein mubtala they, jaisey abu-Ash'hab ki hadis hai aur unhon-ne izafa kya is (ibne- Ziyad) ne kaha : aap ne aaj se pahley mujhey ye hadis kyon nahi bayan ki? Hazrat Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine tumhen kabhi hadis nahi sunai, (tum ne hadis ka samaa hi nahi kya (ya farmaya : main tumhen hadis bayan nahi kya karta tha (hadis main tumhara ustad na tha.)"
4731,"abu-Maleeh se riwayat hai ke Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad, Hazrat Maqil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimari mein unke paas gaya, Hazrat Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main tum ko aik hadis bayan karne laga hun aur agar main marzul-maut mein na hota to tumhen ye hadis na sunata, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai : koi ameer nahi jo musalmanon ke maamlon ka zimmedaar ho, phir unke liye jiddo-juhad aur khairkhaahi na karey, magar wo unke sath jannat mein dakhil nahi hoga."
4732,Suwada bin abu-Aswad ne khabar di ke mere walid ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Maaqil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey to Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad unki iyaadat ke liye gaya. (aagey) Hasan Basri ki Hazrat Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah hai.
4733,"Hasan Basri (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne bataya ke Aaiz bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se they, Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad ke paas gaey aur farmaya : mere betey ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : badtareen raai (zimmedar), sakht geer aur zulm karne wala hota hai, tum us se bachna ke tum unmein se ho. usne kaha : aap baithiye : aap to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se chhalni mein bach janey waley aakhiri hissey ki tarah hain. (aakhir mein chunkey tinkey, patthar, bhoosi bach jatey hain, isliye) unhon-ne kaha : kya unmein bhoosi, tinkey, patthar they? ye to unke baad huey aur unke ilawa dusron mein huey."
4734,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne abu-Hayyan se, unhon-ne abu-Zura se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham main ( khutba dene ke liye) khadey huey aur aap ne maale-ghanimat mein khiyanat ka zikr farmaya : aap ne aisi khayanat aur uske mamley ko intihai sangeen qarar diya, phir farmaya : main tum mein se kisi ko qiyamat ke din is tarah aata hua na paon ke uski gardan par oont sawar hokar bilbila raha ho aur wo kahey : Allah ke rasool! meri madad farmaiye, aur main jawab mein kahun : main tumharey liye kuchh karne ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta, maine tumhen (duniya hi mein) haq pahuncha diya tha. main tum mein se kisi shakhs ko is haal mein na paon ke wo qiyamat ke din aaey aur uski gardan par ghoda Sawar ho kar hinhinaa raha ho, wo kahey : Allah ke rasool! meri madad kijiye, aur main kahun ke main tumharey liye kuchh bhi nahi kar sakta , maine tumhen haq pahuncha diya tha. main tum mein se kisi shakhs ko is haal mein na paon ke wo qiyamat ke din aaey aur uski gardan par bakri Sawar ho kar mimiya rahi ho, wo kahey : Allah ke rasool! meri madad kijiye, aur main kahun : main tumharey liye kisi cheez ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta , maine tumhen haq se aagah kar diya tha, main tum mein se kisi shakhs ko roze-qiyamat is haalat mein na dekhun ke uski gardan par kisi shakhs ki jaan Sawar ho aur wo ( zulm ki duhaai detey huey) cheekhein mar rahi ho, aur wo shakhs kahey : Allah ke rasool! meri madad kijiye , aur main kahun : main tumharey liye kuchh nahi kar sakta, maine tumhen sab kuchh bata diya tha. main tum mein se kisi shakhs ko us haal mein na paon ke wo qiyamat ke din aaey aur uski gardan par kapda lada hua phad-phada raha ho, aur wo kahey : Allah ke rasool! meri madad kijiye, main kahun : tumharey liye mere bas mein kuchh nahi, maine tum ko sab kuchh se aagah kar diya tha. main tum mein se kisi shakhs ko is haal mein na paon ke wo qiyamat ke din aaey aur uski gardan par na bolney wala maal (sona chandi) lada hua ho, wo kahey : Allah ke rasool! meri madad kijiye , main kahun : tumharey liye mere paas kisi cheez ka ikhtiyar nahi, maine tum ko) anjam ( ki khabar pahuncha di thi."
4735,"Abdur-Rahim bin Sulaiman ne abu-Hayyan se, Jarir ne unse aur Ammara-bin-Qaqa se, un sab ne Abu-Zaraa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se abu-Hayyan se Ismail ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
4736,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maale-ghanimat mein khayanat ka zikr farmaya aur uski sangini bayan ki aur unhon ( Ayub ( ne poori hadis bayan ki. Hammad ne kaha : phir iske baad maine Yahya-bin-Saeed ko yahi hadis bayan kartey huey suna. unhon-ne jyon ka tyon isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah hamein Ayub ne unse bayan ki thi."
4737,"hamein Abdul-Waris ne bayan kya, kaha : hamein Ayub ne Yahya-bin-Saeed bin hayyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera se un sab ki hadis ki tarah hadis riwayat ki."
4738,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hadis bayan ki, alfaz abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ke hain. padhi. kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Asad ke aik shakhs ko jisey ibne-Lutbiya kaha jata tha, aamil muqarrar kya. padhi. Amr aur ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : zakat ki wsooli par (muqarrar kya). padhi. jab wo (zakat wsool karke) aaya to usne kaha : ye aap logon ke liye hai aur ye mujhey hadiya kya gaya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par khadey huey, Allah Taala ki hamd w sana bayan ki aur farmaya : aik aamil ka haal kya hota hai ke main usko ( zakat wsool karne) bhejta hun aur wo aa kar kehta hai : ye aap logon ke liye hai aur ye mujhey hadiya kya gaya hai, aisa kyon na hua ke ye apne bap ya apni maa ke ghar mein baithta, phir nazar aata ke usey hadiya diya jata hai ya nahi? us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! tum mein se koi bhi shakhs aisa nahi ke wo us (maal ( mein se (apne liye) kuchh ley , magar wo qiyamat ke din is haalat mein aayega ke usne usey apni gardan par utha rakha hoga, qiyamat ke din oont hoga, bilbila raha hoga, gaaey hogi, dakraa rahi hogi, bakri hogi, mimiya rahi hogi. phir aap ne apne donon hath is qadr buland kiye ke hamein aap ki donon baghlon ke safaid hissey nazar aaey, phir aap ne 2 martaba farmaya : aey Allah ! kya maine ( haq ( pahuncha diya?"
4739,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Aazad ke ibne- (Lutbiya) naam ke aik shakhs ko zakat (ki wsooli) par aamil banaya, wo kuchh maal lekar aaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko diya aur kaha : ye aap logon ka maal hai aur ye hadiya hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : tum apne bap ya apni maa ke ghar mein kyon nahi baithey, phir dekhtey ke tumhen hadiya diya jata hai ya nahi ? phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba dene ke liye khadey huey, phir Sufiyan (bin Uena ( ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
4740,"Hisham ne apne walid se, unhon-ne abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Asad ke aik shakhs ko banu-Sulaim ke sadqaat wsool karne ke liye aamil banaya, usey ibne-Lutbiya kaha jata tha. jab wo maal wsool karke aaya to (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) iske sath hisab kya. wo kehney laga : ye aap logon ka maal hai aur ye hadiya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum sachey ho to apne bap ya apni maa ke ghar mein ja kar kyon na baith gaey taake tumhara hadiya tumharey paas aa jata. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya, Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ki, phir farmaya : amma baad! main tum mein se kisi shakhs ko kisi aisey kaam par aamil banata hun jiski tauliyat ( intizam ( Allah Taala ne mere sipurd ki hai aur wo shakhs aata hai aur kehta hai ke ye tum logon ka maal hai aur ye hadiya hai jo mujhey mila hai. wo shakhs agar sachcha hai to apne bap ya apni maa ke ghar mein kyon na baith gaya taake uska hadiya uske paas aata, Allah ki qasam! tum mein se jo shakhs bhi us maal mein se koi cheez apne haq ke baghair lega, wo qiyamat ke din Allah Taala ke samney us haal mein pesh hoga ke wo cheez usne apni gardan par utha rakhi hogi, main tum mein se kisi bhi shakhs ko zaroor pehchan loonga jo Allah Taala ke samney is haal mein pesh hoga ke usne oont uthaya hoga jo bilbila raha hoga, ya gaaey utha rakhi hogi jo dakra rahi hogi, ya bakri uthai hogi jo mimiya rahi hogi, phir aap ne apne donon hathon ko itna uper uthaya ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aaney lagi, (us waqt) aap farma rahe they : aey Allah! kya maine (tera paigham) pahuncha diya? (abu-Hameed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye sab) meri aankhon ne dekha aur mere kanon ne suna."
4741,"Abda, ibne-Numair aur abu-Muawia, isi tarah abdur-Raheem bin Sulaiman aur Sufiyan sab ne isi sanad ke sath Hisham se riwayat ki. Abda aur ibne-Numair ki hadis mein hai : jab wo aaya to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) uske sath hisab kya, jis tarah abu-Usama ne kaha aur ibne-Numair ki hadis mein ye (bhi) hai : tum logon ko zaroor pata chal jaeyga, Allah ki qasam! us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! tum mein se koi bhi shakhs jo us (maal) mein se koi cheez lega. Sufiyan ki hadis mein ye izafa hai : meri aankh ne dekha aur mere donon kanon ne suna. (hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan kartey huey) kaha : tum log Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se poochh lo, wo bhi mere sath maujood they."
4742,"Abdullah-bin Zakwan yani abu-Zinad se riwayat hai unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko sadqaat par aamil muqarrar kya, wo bahut zyada maal lekar aaya aur kehney laga : ye aap logon ka hai aur ye mujhey bataur hadiya mila hai, phir usi (pichhli hadis ki) tarah bayan kya. Urwa ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap ne ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni? unhon-ne kaha : baraahe-raast aap ke dahane-mubarak se apne kanon tak (aati hui awaz se suni.)"
4743,"Wakee bin-Jarraah ne kaha : hamein Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid ne Qais-bin abi Hazim se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Adi-bin Umaira kandi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : ham tum mein se jis shakhs ko kisi kaam par aamil muqarrar karein aur wo aik sui ya us se badi koi cheez ham se chipa ley to ye khayanat hogi, wo shakhs qiyamat ke din usey sath lekar aayega. (hazrat Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main dekh raha tha, (ye baat sun kar) Ansar mein se kaley rang ka aik aadmi khada hua aur kehney laga : ya Rasulullah ! aap mujh se apna kaam wapas ley lijiye! aap ne farmaya : tumhen kya hua? usne kaha : maine aapko is-is tarah farmatey huey suna hai (main us waeed se darta hun.) aap ne farmaya : main ab bhi yahi kehta hun ke ham tum mein se jis shakhs ko kisi kaam ka aamil banaaein wo har chhoti aur badi cheez ko lekar aaey, uske baad usmein se jo cheez usko di jaey wo ley-ley aur jo cheez us se rok li jaey us se door rahe.'"
4744,"Abdullah-bin-Numair, Muhammad-bin-Bishr aur abu-Usama sab ne kaha : hamein Ismail ne isi sanad ke sath usi ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki."
4745,"Fazal bin-Musa ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin abi Khalid ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Qais-bin abi Hazim ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Adi-bin Umaira kandi (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, un sab ki hadis ki tarah."
4746,"ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya ke Quran Majeed ki aayat : aey eman waalo! Allah ki itaat karo aur rasool ki itaat karo aur unki jo tum mein se ikhtiyar waley hain Hazrat Abdullah-bin Huzafa bin Qais-bin Adi Sehmi (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq nazil hui hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik lashkar main (ameer bana kar) rawana kya tha (ibne-Juraij ne kaha) mujhey Yala bin Muslim ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki."
4747,"Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman ne abu-Zanad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne meri itaat ki usne Allah ki itaat ki aur jisne meri nafarmani ki usne Allah ki nafarmani ki aur jisne ameer ki itaat ki usne meri itaat ki aur jisne ameer ki nafarmani ki usne meri nafarmani ki."
4748,"ibne-Uena ne abu-Zinad se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, unhon-ne ye bayan nahi kya : jisne ameer ki nafarmani ki us ne meri nafarmani ki."
4749,"Yunus ne khabar di ke unhein ibne-Shahab ne khabar di, kaha : hamein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne meri itaat ki us ne Allah ki itaat ki aur jisne meri nafarmani ki us ne Allah ki nafarmani ki aur jisne mere ( muqarrar karda ( ameer ki itaat ki us ne meri itaat ki aur jisne mere ameer ki nafarmani ki us ne meri nafarmani ki."
4750,"Ziyad (bin Sad ( se riwayat hai, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, bilkul usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah ."
4751,"abu-Awana aur Shoba ne Yala bin Ata se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Alqama se ( hadis) suni , unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pichhli hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
4752,"Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sab ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
4753,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula ( aazad karda ghulam ( abu Yunus ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi ( hadis) riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jisne ameer ki itaat ki farmaya, mere ameer ki nahi farmaya, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se Hammam ki riwayat ki hui hadis mein bhi isi tarah hai."
4754,"Abu-Saleh as-samaan se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par (ameer ka hukm ( sunna aur maanna wajib hai, apni mushkil (ki kaifiyat ( mein bhi aur apni aasani mein bhi, apni khushi mein bhi aur apni naakhushi mein bhi aur us waqt bhi jab tum par) kisi aur ko) tarjeeh di ja rahi ho."
4755,"ibne-Idrees ne hamein Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Imran se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Samit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey wasiiyat farmai thi ke main ( ameer ki baat ( sunoon aur itaat karun chahey wo ( ameer ( katey huey aa'za (angon) wala ghulam hi kyon na ho."
4756,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Nazar-bin-Shumail ne hamein Shoba se, unhon-ne abu-Imran se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur hadis mein kaha : chahey wo (ameer) katey huey aazaa (angon) wala habshi ghulam ( hi kyon na ho. ("
4757,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne hamein Shoba se aur unhon-ne abu-Imran se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, jis tarah ibne-Idrees ne kaha : katey huey aaza (angon) wala ghulam ( hi kyon na ho. ("
4758,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yahya bin Husain se, unhon-ne kaha : maine apni daadi se suna, wo bayan karti thin ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hijjatul-wada ke doran mein khutba de rahe they aur aap farma rahe they : agar tum par aik ghulam ko Hakim banaya jaey aur wo kitabullah ke mutabiq tumhari rehnumai karey to uski baat suno aur itaat karo."
4759,"ibne-Bashar ne hamein yahi hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis sunai aur kaha : habshi ghulam ho."
4760,Wakee bin-Jarraah ne hamein Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : katey huey aaza wala habshi ghulam ho.
4761,"Behaz ne hamein Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki : unhon-ne katey huey aaza wala habshi ghulam nahi kaha, aur ye izafa kya : unhon (umme-Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Mina ya Arafaat mein suna."
4762,"Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisa ne Yahya bin Husain se, unhon-ne apni daadi Hazrat Umme- Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine unhein kehtey huey suna : maine Hijjatul-wada main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bahut si baatein irshad farmain, phir maine aapko ye farmatey huey suna : agar tum par aik katey huey aaza (angon) wala ghulam, mera guman hai aap ne kala bhi kaha, Hakim bana diya jaey aur wo tum ko kitabullah ke mutabiq chillaey to uski baat suno aur itaat karo."
4763,"Leis ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman shakhs par Hakim ki baat sunnaa aur uski itaat karna wajib hai, wo baat usko pasand ho ya na-pasand , siwaey iske ke usey gunah ka hukm diya jaey, agar usey gunah ka hukm diya jaey to usmein na sunnaa (jayaz) hai na maanna."
4764,Yahya qattaan aur Abdullah-bin-Numair donon ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4765,"Zubeda ne Sad bin Ubeda se, unhon-ne abu-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik lashkar bheja aur aik shakhs ko unka ameer banaya, us ( ameer ( shakhs ne aag jalaai aur logon se kaha : usmein dakhil ho jao . kuchh logon ne usmein dakhil honey ka irada kar liya aur kuchh logon ne kaha : ham aag hi se to bhaagey hain, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us waqiey ka zikr kya gaya to aap ne un logon se jo aag mein dakhil hona chahtey they, farmaya : agar tum aag mein dakhil ho jatey to qiyamat tak usi mein rahtey aur dusron ke haq main achi baat farmai aur farmaya : Allah Taala ki gunah (nafarmani) mein kisi ki itaat nahi, itaat sirf neki mein hai."
4766,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numair, Zuhair-bin-Harab aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne hadis bayan ki, alfaz sab ke miltey-jultey hain, ( teenon ne) kaha : hamein Wakee ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sad bin Ubeda se, unhon-ne abu Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik lashkar bheja aur Ansar mein se aik aadmi ko unka ameer banaya aur lashkar ko ye hukm diya ke wo uske ehkaam sunein aur uski itaat karein, ( ittifaq se) ahale-lashkar ne kisi baat mein ameer ko naraz kar diya, usne kaha : mere liye lakdiyan jama karo. lashkar ne lakdiyan jama kin, phir usne kaha : aag jalaao , unhon-ne aag jalaai, phir kaha : kya tum ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera hukm sunney aur manney ka hukm nahi diya tha? unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi, usne kaha : aag mein dakhil ho jao, unhon-ne aik doosrey ki taraf dekha aur kaha : ham aag hi se bhag kar to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey they. wo usi mauqif par qaaim rahe yahan tak ke uska ghussa thanda ho gaya aur aag bujhaa di gaee, jab wo lautey to ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai , aap ne farmaya : agar ye log us ( aag ( mein dakhil ho jatey to phir us se bahar na nikaltey, itaat sirf Maruf (qaabile-qabool kaamon) mein hai."
4767,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Wakee aur abu-Muawia ne Aamash se isi sanad se isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
4768,"hamein abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Ubaidullah-bin-Umar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ubada bin Waleed se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne unke dada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath is baat par bait ki ke mushkil mein aur aasani main aur khushi mein aur naakhushi main aur khud par tarjeeh diye janey ki sura mein bhi sunengey aur itaat karengey aur is baat par bait ki ke jinke paas amaarat hogi, amaarat ke mamley mein unse tanaaza nahi karengey aur ham jahan kahin bhi hongey (hamesha) haq kahengey aur Allah ke (deen par chalney ke) mamley mein kisi malaamat karne waley ki malaamat se nahi darengey."
4769,"yahi hadis hamein ibne-Numair ne bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Idris ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne- Ajlan, Ubaidullah-bin-Umar aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubada bin Waleed se isi sanad se usi jaisi hadis bayan ki."
4770,"Yazeed bin haad ne Ubada bin Waleed bin Ubada-bin-Samit, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bait ki, ibne-Idrees ki hadis ki tarah."
4771,"Junaada bin abi Umaya se riwayat hai, kaha : ham Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir huey, wo (is waqt) bimar they, ham ne kaha : Allah Taala aapko sihat ata farmaey, ham ko aisi hadis sunaaiye jis se hamein fayda hua aur jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho, (hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko bulaya, ham ne aap ke sath bait ki, aap ne ham se jin chizon par bait li wo ye thin ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se khushi aur naakhushi main aur mushkil aur aasani main aur ham par tarjeeh diye janey ki sura mein, sunney aur itaat karne par bait ki aur is par ke ham iqtidaar ke mamley mein uski ahliyat rakhney walon se tanaaza nahi karengey. kaha : haan, agar tum usmein khullam khulla kufr dekho jiske (kufr honey par) tumharey paas (Quran aur sunnat se) waazeh aasaar maujood hun."
4772,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ‌ : imam sipar (dhaal) hai iske peechhey musalman ladtey hain ‌ ( kaafiron se) aur uski wjah se log bachtey hain takalluf se (zaalimon se aur luteron se). phir agar wo hukm karey Allah se darney ka aur insaf karey to usko sawab hoga aur jo uske khilaf hukm de dey to is par wabaal hoga.
4773,"Shoba ne hamein Furaat Qazzaz se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se riwayat ki ke main panch saal Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka ham majlis raha, maine unko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye hadis bayan kartey huey suna : bani-Israel ke anbiya unka ijtimaai nizaam chalaatey they, jab aik Nabi faut hota to doosra Nabi iska ja-nashin hota aur (ab) bila shubah mere baad koi Nabi nahi, ab khulafa hongey aur kasarat se hongey. sahaba ne kaha : aap hamein kya hukm detey hain? aap ne farmaya : pahley aur uske baad phir pahley ki bait ke sath wafaa karo, unhein unka haq do aur (tumharey huquq ki) jo zimme-dari unhein di hai iske mutaalliq Allah khud unse sawal karega."
4774,Hasan-bin-Furaat ne apne walid se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
4775,Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ab mere baad) kuchh logon se) tarjeehi sulook hoga aur aisey kaam hongey jinhein tum bura samjhogey. sahaba ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! ham mein se jo shakhs un halaat ka saamna karey uske barey mein aap ka kya hukm hai? aap ne farmaya : tum par (hukkaam ka ( jo haq hai tum usko ada karna aur jo tumhara haq hai wo tum Allah se maangna.
4776,"Abdur-Rehman bin abd rabe-kaba se riwayat hai main masjid mein gaya wahan Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) Kaba ke saaye mein baithey they aur log unke paas jama they mein bhi gaya aur betha. unhon-ne kaha ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aik safar main to aik jagah utrey, koi apna dera durust karne laga, koi teer maarney laga, koi apne janwaron mein tha ke itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pukarney waley ne awaz di Namaz ke liye ikattha ho jao. ham sab aap ke paas jama huey. aap ne farmaya mujh se pahley koi Nabi aisa nahi guzra jis par zaroori na ho apni ummat ko jo behtar baat usko malum ho batana aur jo buri baat ho us se daraana aur tumhari ye ummat iske pahley hisse mein salamati hai aur akheer hissey mein bula hai aur wo baatein hain jo tum ko buri lagengi aur aisey fitney aawengey ke aik fitna doosrey ko halka aur patlaa kar dega (yani baad ka fitna pahley se aisa badh kar hoga ke pahla fitna uske samney kuchh haqiqat na rakhega) aur aik fitna aawega to momin kahega ismein meri tabahi hai phir wo jata rahega aur doosra aawega momin kahega ismein meri tabahi hai. phir jo koi chahey ke jahannam se bachey aur jannat mein jaawey usko chahiye ke marey Allah Taala aur pichhley din par yaqin rakh kar aur logon se wo sulook karey jaisa wo chahta ho ke log us se karein aur jo shakhs kisi imam se bait karey aur usko apna hath de dewey aur dil se niyat karey uski taabedaari ki to uski itaat karey agar taqat ho. ab agar doosra imam us se ladney ko aawey to (usko mana karo agar na maaney baghair ladai ke to) uski gardan maaro. ye sun kar main Abdullah ke paas gaya aur unse kaha, main tum ko qism deta hun Allah ki tum ne ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai? unhon-ne apne kanon aur dil ki taraf ishara kya hath se aur kaha mere kanon ne suna aur dil ne yad rakha. maine kaha tumharey chacha ke betey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ham ko hukm kartey hain aik doosrey ka maal nahaq khaney ke liye aur apni jaanon ko tabah karne ke liye aur Allah farmata hai ''aey eman waalo apne amwaal ko naajaaiz tareeqey se na khaao siwaey iske ke aisi tijarat ho jo baahami raza-mandi se ki jaey aur na apni jaanon ko qatl karo beshak Allah tum par raham farmanewala hai.'' ye sun kar Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) thodi der tak chup rahe phir kaha Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki itaat karo us kaam mein jo Allah ke hukm ke muwafiq ho aur jo kaam Allah Taala ke hukm ke khilaf ho usmein Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka kehna na maano."
4777,Wakee aur abu-Muawia donon ne Aamash se isi sanad se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
4778,"Aamir ne Abdur-Rehman bin abde-rabe-kaba Saaidi se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Kaba ke paas aik majma dekha, phir Aamash ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
4779,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik Ansari ne tanhai main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat ki aur kaha : kya jis tarah aap ne falan shakhs ko aamil banaya hai mujhey aamil nahi banaaengey? aap ne farmaya : mere baad tum khud ko (doosron par) tarjeeh ( dene ka mamla ( dekhogey tum is par sabr kartey rehna , yahan tak ke hauze-kausar par mujh se aan milo. ( wahan tumhen meri shafaat par us sabr w tahammul ka be panah ajr milega. ("
4780,"hamein Khalid-bin Haris ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba bin Hajjaj ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Hazrat Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke aik Ansari ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se tanhai mein baat ki, usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah."
4781,Muaz ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis sunai aur ye nahi kaha is ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se tanhai mein baat ki.
4782,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Alqama bin Waail hizrami se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Salma bin Yazeed jaufi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya aur kaha : Allah ke Nabi! aap kaisey dekhtey hain ke agar ham par aisey log hukmaraan banein jo ham se apne huquq ka mutalba karein aur hamarey haq hamein na dein to is sura mein aap hamein kya hukm detey hain? aap us se bachey, us ne dobara sawal kya, aap ne phir munh pher liya, phir jab us ne dusri ya teesri baar sawal kya to usko Ashas bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne kheench liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suno aur itaat karo kyonke jo zimme-dari unko di gaee iska baar un par hai aur jo zimme-dari tumhen di gaee hai, uska bojh tum par hai."
4783,"Shababa ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur kaha : Ashas bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne us (poochhney waale) ko kheencha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suno aur itaat karo, jo zimme-dari un par dali gaee uska bojh un par hai aur jo tum par dali gaee iska bojh tum par hai."
4784,"Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhali baton ko puchha kartey aur main buri baat ko poochhta us dar se ke kahin burai mein na pad jaun. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! ham jahiliyat aur burai mein they phir Allah ne ham ko ye bhalai di (yani Islam ( ab iske baad bhi kuchh burai hai? aap ne farmaya : haan lekin usmein dhabba hai. maine kaha wo dhabba kaisa? aap ne farmaya aisey log hongey jo meri sunnat par nahi chalengey aur mere tareeqe ke siwa aur raah par chalengey, unmein achi baatein bhi hongi aur buri bhi. maine arz kya phir iske baad burai hogi? aap ne farmaya haan aisey log paida hongey jo jahannam ke darwazey ki taraf logon ko bulaawengey, jo unki baat maanega usko jahannam mein daal dengey. maine kaha ya Rasulullah! un logon ka haal ham se bayan farmaiye? aap ne farmaya unka rang hamara sa hi hoga aur hamari hi zaban bolengey. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! agar us zamane ko main paon to kya karun? aap ne farmaya musalmanon ki jamat ke sath reh aur unke imam ke sath reh. kaha agar jamat aur imam na hon? aap ne farmaya to sab firqon ko chhod de aur agarche aik darakht ki jad daant se chabaata rahe martey dam tak."
4785,"Huzefa bin Yaman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! ham burai mein they phir Allah Taala ne bhalai di ab iske baad bhi kuchh burai hai? aap ne farmaya : haan. maine kaha phir iske baad bhalai hai aap ne farmaya haan maine kaha phir iske baad burai ? aap ne farmaya haan. maine kaha kaisey ? aap ne farmaya mere baad wo log Hakim hongey jo meri raah par na chalengey , meri sunnat par amal nahi karengey aur unmein aisey log hongey jinke dil shaitan ke se aur badan aadmiyon ke se hongey. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! us waqt main kya karun? aap ne farmaya agar to aisey zamane mein ho to sun aur maan Hakim ki baat ko agarche wo teri peeth phodey aur tera maal le-ley par uski baat suney ja aur uska hukm maanta reh."
4786,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs Hakim ki itaat se bahar ho jaawey aur jamat ka sath chhod de phir wo marey to uski maut jahiliyat ki si hogi aur jo shakhs andhey jhandey ke taley ladey (jis ladai ki durusti shariat se saaf-saaf Sabit na ho) ghussa ho qaum ke lihaaz se ya bulata ho qaum ki taraf ya madad karta ho qaum ki aur khuda ki razamandi maqsud na ho phir maara jaawey to uska maara jana jahiliyat ke zamaney ka sa hoga aur jo shakhs (meri ummat par) dast daraazi karey aur achchhey aur buron ko unmein ke qatl karey aur momin ko bhi na chhodey aur jis se ahad hua ho iska ahad pura na karey to wo mujh se ilaqa nahi rakhta aur main us se talluq nahi rakhta (yani wo musalman nahi hai).
4787,tarjama wahi hai jo uper guzra.
4788,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs itaat se nikal jaawey aur jamat chhod de phir marey to uski maut jahiliyat ki si hogi, aur jo shakhs takleef deney waaley jhandey ke taley maara jaawey jo ghussa hota ho qaum ke paas se aur ladtaa ho qaum ke khayal se wo meri ummat mein se nahi hai aur jo meri ummat par nikley maarta hua unke nekon aur badon ko, kisi momin ko bhi na chhodey, jisse ahad ho wo bhi pura na karey to wo meri ummat mein nahi hai."
4789,tarjama wahi hai jo uper guzra .
4790,Ibne-Abbas (raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs apne Hakim se buri baat dekhey wo sabr karey isliye ke jo jamat se baalisht bhar juda ho jaawey uski maut jahiliyat ki maut hogi.
4791,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs apne Hakim se buri baat dekhey wo sabr karey kyonke jo koi badshah se baalisht bhar juda ho phir marey usi haal mein, uski maut jahiliyat ki si maut hogi."
4792,Jundub bin-Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs andhey jhandey ke taley maara jaawey aur wo bulata ho tassub aur qaumi tarafdaar ki taraf ya madad karta ho qaumi ta'ssub ki to uska qatl jahiliyat ka sa hoga.
4793,"Naafe se riwayat hai Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Abdullah-bin mutee ke paas aaey jab Harra ka waqia hua Yazeed bin Muawiya ke zamane mein us ne Madina munawara par lashkar bheja aur Madina waley Harra mein jo aik maqam hai Madina se mila hua qatl huey is tarah ke zulm Madina walon par huey. Abdullah-bin mutee ne kaha abu Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) (ye kunniyat hai Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki) ke liye to shak (gadda) bichhaao. unhon-ne kaha, main isliye nahi aaya ke baithun balke aik hadis tujh ko sunaney ke liye aaya hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai, aap farmatey they jo shakhs apna hath nikal ley itaat se wo qiyamat ke din khuda se milega aur koi daleel uske paas na hogi aur jo shakhs mar jaawey aur kisi se us ne bait na ki ho to uski maut jahiliyat ki si hogi."
4794,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra.
4795,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra .
4796,"Shoba ne Ziyad bin Ilaqa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Arfaja (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jald hi fitnon par fitney barpa hongey, to jo shakhs is ummat ke mamley (nizame-saltanat) ko tukdey-tukdey karna chahey jabke wo muttahid ho to usey talwaar ka nishana bana do, wo jo koi bhi ho, so ho."
4797,"abu-Awana , Sheban 'Israel' Abdullah-bin Mukhtar aur aik aadmi jiska Hammad ne naam liya tha, un sab ne Ziyad bin Ilaqa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Arfaja (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, magar un sab ki hadis mein : usey qatl kar do ke alfaz hain."
4798,"abu Yaafoor ne Hazrat Arfaja (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jab tumhara nizaam ( hukumat ( aik shakhs ke zimmey ho, phir koi tumharey ittihaad ki laathi ko todney ya tumhari jamat ko muntashir karne ke iraadey se aagey badhey to usey qatl kar do."
4799,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab 2 khaleefon ke liye bait li jaey to unmein se doosrey ko qatl kar do."
4800,"Hammam bin Yahya ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hasan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne zaba bin Mohsin se, unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jald hi aisey hukmaraan hongey ke tum unhein (kuchh kaamon mein) sahi aur (kuchh mein) ghalat paogey jisne (unki rehnumai mein) nek kaam kiye wo bari thehra aur jisne (unke ghalat kaamon se) inkar kar diya wo bach gaya lekin jo har kaam par razi hua aur (unki) pairwi ki (wo na bari hua na bach saka) sahaba ne kaha : kya ham unse jang na karein? aap ne farmaya : nahi, jab tak ke wo Namaz padhtey rahen (jang na karo)"
4801,"Hisham dustwaai ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Hasan ne zaba bin Mohsin Anzi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : tum par aisey ameer lagaey jaeinge jin main tum achchhaiyan bhi dekhogey aur buraaiyan bhi, jisne ( burey kaamon ko) na-pasand kya, wo buri ho gaya, jisne inkar kya wo bach gaya, magar jisne pasand kya aur peechhey laga (wo bari hua na bach saka.) sahaba ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! kya ham unse ladai na karein, aap ne farmaya : nahi, jab tak wo Namaz padhtey rahen. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka maqsad tha jisne dil se na-pasand kya aur dil se bura jaana."
4802,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha : hamein Mu-alla bin Ziyad aur Hisham ne Hasan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne zaba bin Mohsin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pichhli hadis ki tarah, albatta us hadis mein ye alfaz hain : jisne inkar kya, wo bari ho gaya aur jisne na-pasand kya, wo bach gaya."
4803,"ibne-Mubarak ne Hisham se, unhon-ne Hasan se, unhon-ne zaba-bin-Mohsin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir usi ki tarah bayan kya, siwaey in alfaz ke : jisne pasand kya aur peechhey laga ye alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
4804,"Yazeed bin Yazeed bin Jaabir ne Ruzaiq-bin-Hayyan se, unhon-ne Muslim-bin-Qarza se, unhon-ne Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey behtreen imam (khaleefa) wo hain jin se tum mohabbat karo aur wo tum se mohabbat karein, tum unke liye dua karo aur wo tumharey liye dua karein aur tumharey badtareen imam wo hain jin se tum bughz rakho aur wo tum se bughz rakhein, tum un par laanat karo aur wo tum par laanat karein. kaha gaya : Allah ke rasool! kya ham unko talwaar ke zor se phenk ( hata ( na dein? aap ne farmaya : nahi, jab tak ke wo tum mein Namaz qaaim kartey rahen aur jab tum apne hukmaraanon mein koi aisi cheez dekho jisey tum na-pasand kartey ho to uske amal ko na-pasand karo aur uski itaat se dastkash na ho."
4805,"Dawood-bin-rushaid ne kaha : hamein Waleed-bin-Muslim ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed-bin-Jaabir ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey banu-Fazara ke aazad karda ghulam razeeq-bin-hayyaan ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Auf-bin-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha zaad Muslim-bin-Qarza se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : tumharey behtreen imam ( hukmaraan ( wo hain jin se tum mohabbat karo aur wo tum se mohabbat karein, tum unke liye dua karo aur wo tumharey liye dua karein aur tumharey badtareen imam wo hain jin se tum bughz rakho aur wo tum se bughz rakhein aur tum un par laanat karo aur wo tum par laanat karein. (hazrat Auf-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : sahaba ne kaha : kya ham aisey mauqe par unka dat kar muqaabla na karein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, jab tak wo tum mein Namaz qaaim kartey rahen , nahi, jab tak wo tum mein Namaz qaaim kartey rahen. sun rakho ! jis par kisi shakhs ko Hakim banaya gaya, phir us ne us Hakim ko Allah ki kisi gunah (nafarmani) mein mubtala dekha to wo Allah ki us ma'siyat (nafarmani)  ko bura janey aur uski itaat se hargiz hath na kheenchey. ibne- Jaabir ne kaha : maine Ruzeq se, jab unhon-ne mujhey ye hadis bayan ki, puchha : abu Miqdam ! main tum ko Allah ki qism deta hun, waqei unhon-ne ye hadis aapko bayan ki, ya aap ne Muslim-bin-Qarza se suni, jabke wo keh rahe they ke unhon-ne Auf (bin-Malik ( (Raziallahu anhu) se suni aur wo ye keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunaa? kaha : to wo ( Ruzeq ( do zaanu baith gaey aur qibley ki taraf munh kar liya aur kaha is zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi ! maine ye hadis Muslim-bin-Qarza se suni , wo keh rahe they : maine Auf-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
4806,"Ishaq-bin-Musa Ansari ne kaha : hamein Waleed-bin-Muslim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne- Jaabir ne isi sanad se khabar di aur kaha : banu-Fazara ke aazad karda ghulam razeeq. Imam Muslim ne kaha : ye hadis Muawiya-bin-Saleh ne bhi Rabee-bin-Yazeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Muslim-bin-Qarza se, unhon-ne Auf-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4807,"Leis ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hudaibiya ke din ham aik hazaar char sau they, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath par bait ki aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik darakht ke nichey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath thaam rakha tha. wo babool ( keekar (ka darakht tha. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ne is baat par aap se bait ki ke ham faraar na hongey aur ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath par maut ki bait nahi ki."
4808,"Sufiyan ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mar janey par bait nahi ki, ham ne aap se is baat par bait ki thi ke ham faraar na hongey."
4809,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hajjaj ne ibne-Juraij se hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse puchha gaya tha ke Hudaibiya ke din aap logon ki tadaad kitni thi? unhon-ne kaha : ham chaudah sau they. ham ne aik darakht ke nichey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki jabke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ka hath thaam rakha tha. wo babool ka darakht tha, ham sab ne aap se bait ki siwaey jad-bin-Qais Ansari ke , (us ne aap se bait nahi ki) wo apne oont ke pet ke nichey chhup gaya."
4810,"mujhey Ibrahim-bin-Dinar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin-majaalid ke aazad karda ghulam Hujjaj-bin-Muhammad Aawar ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse sawal kiya gaya tha : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zul-Hulaifa mein bait li thi? unhon-ne kaha : nahi, albatta aap ne wahan Namaz padhi thi aur Hudaibiya ke darakht ke siwa aap ne kisi aur darakht ke nichey bait nahi li. ibne-Juraij ne kaha : unhein abu-Zubair ne ye bataya ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ye kehtey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hudaibiya ke kuwein par dua ki thi."
4811,"Amr ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hudaibiya ke din ham aik hazaar char sau they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : aaj tum poori zamin ke behtreen afraad ho. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar main dekh sakta to main tum ko us darakht ki jagah dikhata."
4812,"Amr-bin-Murra ne Saalim-bin-abi-Jaad se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se ashaab shajra (baite-rizwan karne walon ki tadaad (ke mutaalliq poochha, to unhon-ne kaha : agar ham aik laakh bhi hotey to wo (pani) hamein kafi hota lekin ham ( taqriban ( aik hazaar panch sau log they."
4813,"Husain ne Saalim-bin-abi-Jaad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke agar ham aik laakh bhi hotey to wo (pani) hamein kafi hota lekin ham ( taqriban ( pandarah sau they."
4814,"Aamash ne kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-abi-Jaad ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha is din aap log kitney they? unhon-ne kaha : aik hazaar char sau. (yani bait karne waley)"
4815,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Umra-bin-Murra se hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke ashaab shajra terah (13) sau they aur qabila Aslam ke log muhajireen ka aathwan hissey they. (unhon-ne ye tadaad andaazey se batai.)"
4816,Abu-Dawud aur Nazar-bin-Shumail ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
4817,"Khalid ( Hazza ( ne hukm-bin-Abdullah-bin-Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine (baite-rizwan ke din apne aapko us haalat mein dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon se bait ley rahe they aur maine us darakht ki shakhon mein se aik shaakh ko aap ke sar anwar se uper utha rakha tha, ham us waqt chaudah sau they. unhon-ne kaha : ham ne (is mauqe par) aap se maut par bait nahi ki thi, ham ne ye bait ki thi ke ham faraar nahi hongey."
4818,"Yunus ne isi sanad se, yani hukm-bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki."
4819,"abu-Awana ne Tariq se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat ki, kaha : mere walid bhi un logon mein se they jinhoney darakht ke nichey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi. unhon-ne kaha : jab ham agley saal Haj ke liye gaey to hamein uski jagah nahi mili , agar tum logon ko wo jagah malum ho gaee hai to tum log zyada jaanney waley ho."
4820,"Sufiyan ne taariq-bin-Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke (baite-rizwan ke saal wo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, phir agley saal wo log us darakht ko bhool chukey they."
4821,"Qatada ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : maine wo darakht dekha tha, phir main iske baad wahan gaya to main us darakht ko na pehchan saka."
4822,"Hatim-bin-Ismail ne Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Yazeed-bin-Ubaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Hudaibiya ke din tum logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kis cheez par bait ki thi? unhon-ne kaha : maut par."
4823,Hammad-bin-Masada ne kaha hamein Yazeed ne Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ‌ se usi ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki hai.
4824,"Ibad-bin-Tameem ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : unke paas koi shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : ibne-Hanzala logon se bait ley rahe hain? puchha : kis cheez par? kaha : maut par. kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad kisi shakhs ke sath is baat par bait nahi karunga."
4825,"Yazeed-bin-abi-Ubaid ne Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo Hajjaj ke paas gaey, usne kaha : ibne-Akwaa ! kya aap wapas pichhli ravish par lot gaey hain, baadiya mein rehney lagey hain? unhon-ne kaha : nahi (pichhli ravish par nahi lota ( lekin mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baadiya mein rehney ki ijazat di thi."
4826,"Ismail-bin-Zakariya ne Aasim ahwal se, unhon-ne abu-Usman nehdi se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat mujaashea'-bin-Masood Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hijrat par bait karne ke liye aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hijrat ki bait karne walon ka waqt guzar gaya, albatta Islam , jihad aur khair par bait ( jaaiz ( hai."
4827,"Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne Aasim se, unhon-ne abu-Usman se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey mujaashea'-bin-Masood Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, kaha : main apne bhai abu-Ma'bad (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath fateh (Makka) ke baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! is se hijrat par bait ley lijiye, aap ne farmaya : hijrat walon ke sath hijrat (ka marhala ( guzar gaya. maine kaha : phir aap kis baat par us se bait lengey ? aap ne farmaya : Islam , jihad aur khair par. abu-Usmaan ne kaha : meri Hazrat abu Mabad (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui to maine unko Hazrat mujaashea' (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha is ne sach kaha hai."
4828,"Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne Aasim se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, kaha : main Hazrat majaashea' (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhai se mila, unhon-ne kaha is ne sach kaha, abu-Ma'bad (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kiya."
4829,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : fateh ke din jab Makka fateh hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ab hijrat nahi hai, lekin jihad aur niyat hai aur jab tum ko jihad ke liye bulaya jaey to niklo."
4830,"Sufiyan , Mufazzal-bi-muhalhil aur Israel , sab ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4831,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hijrat ke mutaalliq sawal kiya gaya, aap ne farmaya : fateh (Makka) ke baad hijrat nahi hai, lekin jihad aur niyat hai aur jab tum ko jihad ke liye bulaya jaey to niklo."
4832,"Waleed-bin-Muslim ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Amr Auzai ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey ibne-Shahab Zohri ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne un sab ko hadis sunai, kaha : Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke aik dehati ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hijrat ke mutaalliq sawal kiya. aap ne farmaya : tum par afsos ! hijrat ka mamla to bahut mushkil hai. kya tumharey paas kuchh oont hain? usne kaha : haan , aap ne farmaya : kya tum unki zakat ada kartey ho? usne kaha : haan , aap ne farmaya : paaniyon ( chashmon , daryaon , samandaron wghaira) ke paar ( rahtey huey) amal kartey raho to bila shubah Allah Taala tumharey kisi amal ko hargiz rayegaan (bekar) nahi karega ."
4833,"Muhammad-bin-Yousuf ne Auzai se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki magar unhon-ne kaha : bila shubah Allah Taala tumharey amal mein se kisi cheez ko zaaya nahi karega aur ye izafa kiya, aap ne farmaya : jis din oontniyan pani peeney ke liye ( ghaat ya chashmey par) aati hain to kya tum ( zarurat mandon , miskinon , musaafiron ko pilaaney ke liye) unka doodh dohtey ho? usne kaha : haan."
4834,"Younus-bin-Yazeed ne kaha : ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : musalman auratein jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aatin to Allah ke us farman ke mutabiq unka imtihaan liya jata : aey Nabi ! jab aap ke paas musalman auratein aaein, aap se is par bait karein ke wo kisi ko Allah ka Sharik nahi banaein gi, na chori karengi aur na zina karengi aayat ke aakhir tak. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : momin aurton mein se jo aurat in baton ka iqrar kar leti , wo imtihaan ke zariey se iqrar karti ( maslan : unse sawal kiya jata : kya tum shirk nahi karo gi? to agar wo kehtin : nahi karengi , to yahi unka iqrar hota, aayat ke aakhiri hissey tak isi tarah imtihaan aur iqrar hota. (aur jab wo un baton ka iqrar kar letin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse farmatey : jao, main tum se bait ley chuka hun. Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath kabhi kisi aurat ke hath ko nahi laga balke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke sath baat karke bait kartey they. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse un baton ke ilawa kisi cheez ka ahad nahi liya jinka Allah Taala ne aapko hukm diya tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hatheli kabhi kisi aurat ki hatheli se ragdi nahi, aap jab unse bait letey to zabani farma detey : maine tum se bait ley li."
4835,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein aurton ki bait ke mutaalliq bataya , kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi kisi aurat ko apne hath se nahi chhuwa , albatta aap unse ( zabani ( ahad letey they aur jab wo ahad kar letin to aap farmatey : jao, maine tum se bait ley li."
4836,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : ham sunney aur itaat karne par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait kartey they aur aap ham se farmatey they : ( kaho : ( jiski mujhey istitaat (taqat) hogi."
4837,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jang (ke mamley) mein mera muaayna farmaya, us waqt meri umr chaudah saal thi, aap ne mujhey ( jang mein shumooliyat ki) ijazat nahi di aur Khandaq ki jang ke din mera muaayna farmaya jabke mein pandarah baras ka tha to aap ne mujhey ijazat de di. Naafe ne kaha : jis zamaney mein Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez khaleefa they maine unke paas ja kar ye hadis bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha : ye sagheer ( nabaligh (aur kabir ( baligh (ke darmyan had ( faasil ( hai. phir unhon-ne apne aamilon ko likh bheja ke jo shakhs pandarah saal ka ho uska ( pura ( hissey muqarrar karein aur jo us se kam ka ho usko bachchon mein shumaar karein. (uske mutabiq wazeefa dein.)"
4838,"Abdullah-bin-Idris , abdur-Raheem-bin-Sulaiman aur abdul-wahaab Saqafi sab ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar unki hadis mein hai : aur jab main chaudah saal ka tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey kam-sin qarar diya."
4839,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dushman ke mulk mein Quraan Majeed ko sath lekar safar karne se mana farmaya."
4840,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is khof ki bina par ke dushman ke hath lag jaeyga, dushman ki sarzameen mein Quraan Majeed ko sath lekar safar karne se mana farmatey they."
4841,"Hammad ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Quraan ke sath safar na karo, kyonke mujhey is baat par itminan nahi ke wo dushman ke hath lag jaeyga Ayub ne kaha : Quraan Majeed dushman ke hath lag gaya to wo Quraan Majeed ke zariey se ( usey aad bana kar) tumharey sath muqaabla karega."
4842,"Ismail-bin-Ulaih , Sufiyan aur Saqafi sab ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, Ayub aur Suhak-bin-Usman ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. ibne-Ulaih aur Saqafi ki hadis mein hai : mujhey khof hai aur Sufiyan aur Suhak-bin-Usman ki hadis mein hai : is khof se ke dushman ke hath lag jaey."
4843,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisey ghodon ki hafiya ke maqam se musaabiqat (daud) karwaai jinhein (arabi tareeqey se) faaltu charbi zaayel (khatm) karke tez chalne ke liye sadhaya gaya tha. unki daud saniyatul-wadaa' tak thi aur jinko tez chalne ke liye sadhaya nahi gaya tha unki daud saniya se masjid bani zuraiq tak karai. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) unmein shamil they jinhoney ghodey daudaey."
4844,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Muhammad-bin-Rumeh aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne Lais-bin-Sad se hadis bayan ki. Khalaf-bin-Hisham, abu-Rabe aur abu-Kamil ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki. Zuhair ne kaha : hamein Ismail ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki. Abdullah-bin-Numair , abu-Usama aur Yahya qattaan sab ne Ubaidullah se riwayat ki. Ali-bin hijr , Ahmad-bin-Abda aur ibne-abi-Umar ne mujhey hadis sunai, sab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Ismail-bin-Umayya se hadis sunai. ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Musa-bin-Aqba ne khabar di. ibne-Wahab ne kaha : mujhey Usama-bin-Zaid ne khabar di. un sab ( Lais-bin-Sad , Ayub , Ubaidullah , Ismail-bin-Umayya , Musa-bin-Aqba aur Usama-bin-Zaid ( ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Malik ki Naafe se riwayat ki hui hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki, Hammad aur ibne-Ulaih ki Ayub se riwayat mein ye izafa kiya : Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main awwal aaya aur ghoda mujh samet masjid (banu- zuraiq) se aagey nikal gaya. (jahan pahunchnaa tha, tez raftaari ki bina par us jagah se aagey nikal gaya.)"
4845,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodon ki peshani mein barkat hai aur khoobi qiyamat tak.''
4846,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra .
4847,Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap aik ghodey ki peshani ke baal ungli se mal rahe they aur farmatey they ghodon ki peshaniyon se barkat bandhi hui hai qiyamat tak yani sawab aur ghaneemat.
4848,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra .
4849,"Urwa baariqi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya barkat bandhi hui hai, ghodon ki peshaaniyon se qiyamat tak yani sawab aur ghaneemat."
4850,Urwa baariqi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya barkat bandhi hui hai ghodon ki peshaaniyon se. logon ne arz kiya kis tarah ya Rasulullah ! aap ne farmaya sawab hai aur ghaneemat qiyamat tak (kyonke jihad qaaim rahega qiyamat tak).
4851,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra .
4852,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra is riwayat mein sawab aur ghaneemat ka zikr nahi hai.
4853,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra is riwayat mein sawab aur ghaneemat ka zikr nahi hai.
4854,Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya barkat ghodon ki peshaaniyon mein hai.
4855,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra .
4856,"Wakee ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Salam-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodon mein shikaal ko na-pasand farmatey they. ( shikaal ka mafhoom agli hadis mein bayan hua hai.)"
4857,Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Abdur-Razzaq ne Sufiyan se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki. aur Abdur-Razzaq ki hadis mein ye izafa kiya : shikaal ye hai ke ghodey ke daahiney paon aur baain hath mein safedi ho ya daain hath aur baain paon mein safedi ho ( ulti taraf ke aagey aur peechhey do qadam safaid hon.)
4858,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Wahab-bin-Jareer ne hamein Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Yazeed Nakhai se, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki jis tarah Wakee ki hadis hai. aur Wahab ki riwayat mein) sanad us tarah) hai : unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Yazeed se riwayat ki lekin Nakhai ka zikr nahi kiya."
4859,"Jarir ne umara-bin-Qaqa se, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne khud ( aisey shakhs ki) zamanat di hai ke jo shakhs uske rastey mein nikla , mere rastey mein jihad , mere sath imaan aur mere rasulon ki tasdeeq ke siwa aur kisi cheez ne usey ghar se nahi nikala , uski mujh par zamanat hai ke main usey jannat mein dakhil karunga, ya phir usey uski usi qiyam gaah mein wapas ley aaoonga jis se wo (meri khaatir) nikla tha. jo ajr aur ghaneemat us ne hasil ki wo bhi usey hasil hogi. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! jo zakhm bhi Allah ki raah mein lagaya jata hai (to zakhm khaney wala ( qiyamat ke din usi haalat mein aayega jis haalat mein usko zakhm laga tha, us (zakhm) ka rang khoon ka hoga aur khushbu kastoori ki. aur us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar musalmanon par dushwar na hota to main Allah ki raah mein jihad karne waley kisi bhi lashkar se mukhtalif rawaiya apnaatey huey (ghar mein) na baithta, lekin mere paas itni wusat nahi hoti ke main sab musalmanon ko sawariyan muhaiya kar sakun aur na hi un (sab) ke paas itni wusat hoti hai aur ye baat unko bahut sakht guzarti hai ke wo mujh se peechhey reh jaaein. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! mujhey ye pasand hai ke main Allah ki raah mein jihad karun aur qatl kar diya jaun , phir jihad karun phir qatl kar diya jaun aur phir jihad karun phir qatl kar diya jaun."
4860,ibne-Fuzail ne Umara se isi sanad ke sath (yahi) hadis bayan ki.
4861,"Mugheera-bin-Abdur-Rehman hazami ne abu-Zinad se khabar di, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, farmaya : jis shakhs ne Allah ki raah mein jihad kiya, usey apne ghar se Allah ki raah mein jihad aur us kalimey ki tasdeeq ke ilawa aur kisi cheez ne nahi nikala to Allah uske liye is baat ka kafeel bana hai ke (shaheed ho gaya to) usey jannat mein dakhil karega ya phir us ghaneemat aur ajr samet jo usey mila, uske usi thikaaney mein usko wapas ley jaeyga jahan se wo (jihad ke liye) nikla tha."
4862,"Amr Naqid aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu-Zinad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne-abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, farmaya : koi shakhs Allah ki raah mein zakhmi nahi kiya gaya aur Allah khub janta hai ke uski raah mein kisey zakhmi kiya gaya magar wo qiyamat ke din is tarah aayega ke uske zakhm se khoon umad raha hoga. rang khoon ka hoga aur khushbu kastoori ki."
4863,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin. unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye thi : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har zakhm jo musalman ko Allah ki raah mein lagaya jata hai, qiyamat ke din phir isi tarah apni usi haalat mein hoga jis tarah zakhm lagtey waqt tha. us se khoon tapak raha hoga, uska rang khoon ka hoga aur khushbu kastoori jaisi hogi. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar ye ( dar ( na hota ke main musalmanon ko mashaqqat mein daalun ga to main Allah ki raah mein ladney waley kisi bhi lashkar se peechhey na betha rehta, lekin main itni wusat nahi paata ke main un (musalmanon) ko sawaariyaan muhaiya karun na unke paas itni wusat hai ke wo sawaariyaan muhaiya karke mere peechhey aaein, unke dil is par) bhi) razi nahi hotey ke wo mere peechhey gharon mein baithe rahen."
4864,"ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : agar ye baat na hoti ke main musalmanon ko mashaqqat mein mubtala karunga to main kisi lashkar se peechhey na rehta . unki hadis ki tarah aur isi sanad ke sath (aur is mein ye alfaz bhi hain : (us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! main chahta hun ke Allah ki raah mein qatl kiya jaun , phir zinda kiya jaun Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se Abu-Zaraa ki riwayat ki hui hadis ke mutabiq ."
4865,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar ye ( khadsha ( na hota ke main apni ummat ko mushkil mein daalun ga to mujhey ye pasand tha ke main kisi lashkar se peechhey na rahoon . un sab ki hadis ki manind (tarah)."
4866,"Suhel ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein nikla , Allah uske liye is baat ki zamanat deta hai ''se lekar mein Allah ki raah mein ladney waley kisi lashkar se peechhey na rehta tak.''"
4867,"abu-Khalid Ahmar ne hamein Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qatada aur humaid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, farmaya : koi bhi Rooh rakhne wala jo faut ho jaey aur Allah Taala ke yahan uske liye bhalai maujood ho, ye baat pasand nahi karta ke wo duniya mein wapas jaey ya duniya aur jo kuchh bhi duniya mein hai, usko mil jaey, siwaey Shahid ke , sirf wo shahadat ki jo fazeelat dekhta hai. uski wjah se is baat ki tamanna karta hai ke wo duniya mein wapas jaey aur Allah ki raah mein (dobara) Shahid kiya jaey."
4868,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, aap ne farmaya : jannat mein dakhil honey wala koi bhi shakhs aisa nahi jo ye pasand karta ho ke wo duniya mein wapas jaey, ya zamin par maujood koi cheez uski ho jaey. siwaey Shahid ke , wo (apni ( jo izzat afzaai dekhta hai iski bina par ye tamanna karta hai ke wo das baar wapas jaey aur qatl kiya jaey."
4869,"Khalid-bin-Abdullaah waasti ne Suhail-bin-abi-Saleh se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki raah mein jihad ke barabar kon sa amal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum uski istitaat nahi rakhtey. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : sahaba ne do ya teen baar sawal dohraya , aap ne har baar farmaya : tum iski istitaat nahi rakhtey. teesri baar farmaya : Allah ki raah mein jihad karne waley ki misal us shakhs ki si hai jo roze-daar ho, Allah ke samney uski aayaton ke sath raaton ko khada bhi ho raha ho, wo us waqt tak na rozey mein waqfa aaney de, na Namaz mein yahan tak ke Allah ki raah mein jihad karne wala wapas aa jaey."
4870,"abu-Awana , Jarir aur abu-Muawiya sab ne isi sanad ke sath Suhel se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4871,"abu-Tooba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Muawiya-bin-Salam ne Zaid-bin-salam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Salam se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member ke paas tha ke aik shakhs ne kaha : Islam laney ke baad agar main sirf haajiyon ko pani pilaaun aur uske siwa koi doosra amal na karun to mujhey koi parwah nahi. doosrey ne kaha : Islam laney ke baad agar main sirf Masjide-Haram ko abad karun aur uske siwa aur koi doosra amal na karun to mujhey koi parwah nahi. teesrey ne kaha : jo tum sab ne kaha us se Allah ki raah mein jihad karna afzal hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko danta aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member ke paas awaz unchi na karo. (phir bataya ke) wo Jumey ka din tha. lekin (Jumey se pahley guftgu karne ke bajaey) jab maine Juma padh liya to haazire-khidmat hunga aur jiske barey main tum jhagad rahe ho iske barey mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochhoon ga , to (is mauqe par) Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari (hui) thi (jo aap ne sunai ( : kya tum haajiyon ko pani pilana aur Masjide-Haram ko abad karna us shakhs ke (amal ( jaisa samajhtey ho jo Allah aur yaum aakhirat par imaan laya (aur us ne Allah ke rastey mein jihad kiya? ( aayat ke aakhir tak."
4872,"Yahya-bin-Hassan ne kaha : hamein Muawiya ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Zaid ne khabar di ke unhon-ne abu-Salam se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member ke paas betha tha, jis tarah abu-Tooba ki hadis hai."
4873,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : subah ko ya Sham ko aik baar Allah ki raah mein nikalna duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai, us se behtar hai."
4874,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-abi-Hazim ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Allah ki raah mein banda subah ke waqt jo aik safar karta hai (jis waqt safar karna aasan bhi hota hai) to wo duniya aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai us se behtar hai."
4875,"Sufiyan ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Allah ki raah mein subah ke waqt ka aik safar ya Sham ke waqt ka aik safar , duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai, us se behtar hai."
4876,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar meri ummat mein aisey log na hotey . (jo jihad par janey ke liye intihai zaroori saman muhaiya nahi kar saktey aur na main unke liye muhaiya kar sakta hun) phir aap ne guftgu farmai, usmein aap ne farmaya : Allah ki raah mein subah ka aik safar karna ya Sham ka aik safar karna duniya aur jo kuch is mein hai us se behtar hai."
4877,"Abdullah-bin-Yazeed muqri ne Saeed-bin-abi-Ayub se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Shurehbeel-bin-Sharik muaafiri ne abu-Abdur-Rehman hubli se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki raah mein aik baar subah ko ya Sham ko nikalnaa (ya pahra dena ( un tamam chizon se behtar hai jin par suraj tuloo hota hai aur ghurub hota hai."
4878,"Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Ayub aur Hewa-bin-shureh ne bataya , donon mein se har aik ne kaha : mujhey Shurehbeel-bin-Sharik ne abu-Abdur-Rehman habli se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bilkul pichhli riwayat ki tarah."
4879,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : abu-Saeed ! jo shakhs Allah ke rab honey, Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Nabi honey par (dil ki gahraaiyon) se razi ho gaya, uske liye jannat wajib ho gaee. Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye baat achi lagi to kehney lagey : Allah ke rasool ! yahi baat mere samney dobara irshad farmaein , aap ne aisa hi kiya, iske baad farmaya : aik baat aur bhi hai jiski wjah se bandey ko sau darjey rafa't (bulandi) bakhshi jati hai aur har do darjon mein zamin aur aasman jitna fasla hai. kaha : (maine kaha) Allah ke rasool ! wo ( baat ( kya hai? aap ne farmaya : Allah ke rastey mein jihad karnaa, Allah ke rastey mein jihad karna."
4880,"Leis ne Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed ( Maqbari ( se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se, unhon-ne abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne unhein (abu-Qataada (Raziallahu anhu) ko) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba kiram mein (khutba dene ke liye) khadey huey aur unhein bataya : Allah ki raah mein jihad karna aur Allah par imaan lana (baqi) tamam aamal se afzal hai. aik shakhs khada hua aur kehney laga : Allah ke rasool ! aap kya farmatey hain? agar main Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diya jaun to kya us se mere gunah mujh se door hata diye jaeinge ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : haan , agar tum Allah ki raah mein is haalat mein Shahid kar diye jao ke tum sabr karne waley (datey huey) ho, sirf Allah ki raza chahtey ho, aagey badh rahe ho, peeth pher kar na bhag rahe ho. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne kis tarah kaha tha? usne kaha (maine is tarah kaha tha) : aap kya farmatey hain? agar main Allah ki raah mein Shahid kiya jaun to kya mere gunah mujh se door hata diye jaengey. aap ne farmaya : haan , agar tum is haalat mein Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diye jao ke sabr karne waley (datey huey) ho, sirf Allah ki raza chahtey ho, aagey badh rahe ho, peeth pher kar bhaagney waley nahi, (to sarey gunah mitaa diye jaeinge ( siwaey qarz ke. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne (abhi aa kar) mujh se ye kaha hai."
4881,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed Maqbari se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se, unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kehney laga : aap kya farmatey hain? agar main Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diya jaun. (aagey) Leis ki hadis ke ham mana (hadis bayan ki.)"
4882,"Amr-bin-Dinar aur Muhammad-bin-Ajlan ne Muhammad-bin-Qais se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se, unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, un (Amr aur ibne- Ajlan) mein se aik apne doosrey sathi se kuchh zyada bayan karta hai ke aik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aap member par they, usne kaha : aap kya farmatey hain ke agar main apni talwaar se waar karun? ( kaafir ko qatl karun phir Shahid kar diya jaun , aagey ( Maqbari ki hadis ke ham mana ( hadis bayan ki.)"
4883,"Mufazzal-bin-fazaala ne Abbas qitbaani ke betey Ayash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Yazeed-abu-Abdur-Rehman habli se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Shahid ka har gunah maaf kar diya jata hai, siwaey qarz ke."
4884,"Saeed-bin-abi-Ayub ne kaha : mujhey Ayash-bin-Abbas qatbaani ne abu-Abdur-Rehman habli se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki raah mein qatl kiye janey se qarz ke siwa baqi tamam gunah mitaa diye jatey hain."
4885,"Masruq bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se us aayat ki tafseer malum ki : jo log Allah ki raah mein Shahid kiye gaey unko marey huey na samjho , wo apne rab ke yahan zinda hain, unko rizq diya jata hai. Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham ne bhi iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kiya tha, aap ne farmaya : unki roohein sabz parindon ke andar rehti hain, unke liye arsh ilahi ke sath qindeelein latki hui hain. wo roohein jannat mein jahan chaahein khaati-peeti hain, phir un qindeelon ki taraf lot aati hain, unke rab ne uper se unki taraf jhank kar dekha aur farmaya : kya tumhen kisi cheez ki khahish hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : ham (aur ( kya khahish karein, ham jannat mein jahan chahtey hain ghoomtey aur khaatey peetey hain. Allah ne teen baar aisa kiya ( jhank kar dekha aur poochha.) jab unhon-ne dekha ke unko chhoda nahi jaeyga, unse sawal hota rahega to unhon-ne ne kaha : aey hamarey rab ! ham ye chahtey hain ke hamari ruhon ko hamarey jismon mein lota diya jaey yahan tak ke ham dobara teri raah mein Shahid kiye jaaein. jab Allah Taala ye dekhega ke unko koi hajat nahi hai to unko chhod diya jaeyga."
4886,"Muhammad-bin-Waleed Zubaidi ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur puchha : logon mein se kon sa shakhs afzal hai? aap ne farmaya : jo apne maal aur jaan ke sath Allah ki raah mein jihad karta hai. us ne puchha : iske baad phir kon afzal hai? aap ne farmaya : wo momin afzal hai jo kisi pahaad ki ghatiyon mein se aik ghaati mein rehta hai, Allah ki ibadat karta hai aur logon ko apni burai se mehfooz rakhta hai."
4887,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne puchha : Allah ke rasool ! logon mein se afzal kon hai? aap ne farmaya : aisa momin jo apni jaan aur maal se Allah Taala ki raah mein jihad karta hai. us ne puchha : iske baad ? aap ne farmaya : phir wo aadmi jo pahaad ki ghatiyon mein se kisi ghaati mein tanha rehta hai, apne rab ki ibadat karta hai aur logon ko apne shar se mehfooz rakhta hai."
4888,"Auzai ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur aadmi jo kisi ghaati mein hai kaha, phir wo aadmi nahi kaha."
4889,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Azeez-bin-abi-Hazim ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ba'aja se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logon ke liye zindagi ke behtreen tariqon mein se ye hai ke aadmi ne Allah ke rastey mein jihad ke liye ghodey ki lagaam pakad rakhi ho, uski peeth par Allah ki raah mein udtaa ( tezi se harkat karta ( phirey , jab bhi) dushman ki) aahat ya ( kisi ke) darney ki awaz suney , ud kar wahan pahunch jaey, har us jagah qatl aur maut ko talash karta ho jahan uske honey ka guman ho. ya phir wo aadmi jo bakriyon ke chhotey se rewad ke sath un chotiyon mein se kisi aik choti par ya un wadiyon mein se kisi wadi mein ho, Namaz qaaim karey, zakat de aur yaqeeni anjam ( maut ( tak apne rab ki ibadat karey, achai ke maamlaat ke siwa logon se koi talluq na rakhey ."
4890,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne Abdul-Azeez-bin-abi-Hazim se, unhon-ne aur Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman donon ne isi sanad ke sath abu-Hazim se usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki (ba'aja ka mukammal naam letey huey) ba'aja-bin-Abdullah-bin-badr kaha, aur Yahya ki riwayat ke bar-aks (un wadiyon mein se aik wadi ke bajaey) un ghatiyon mein se aik ghaati mein kaha."
4891,"Usama-bin-Zaid ne ba'aja-bin-Abdullah Juhni se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ke ham mana hadis riwayat ki jo abu-Hazim ne ba'aja se riwayat ki. aur unhon-ne ghatiyon mein se aik ghaati mein kaha."
4892,"Muhammad-bin-abi-Umar Makki ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala do aadmiyon ki taraf (dekh kar) hansta hai, un donon mein se aik aadmi doosrey ko qatl karta hai aur donon jannat mein dakhil ho jatey hain. sahaba kiram ne puchha : Allah ke rasool ! ye kaisey (mumkin) hai? aap ne farmaya : aik shakhs Allah ki raah mein jang karta hai aur Shahid ho jata hai, phir Allah iske qaatil ko tauba ki taufeeq ata karta hai to wo musalman ho jata hai, phir wo (bhi) Allah ki raah mein jihad karta hai aur Shahid ho jata hai. (jaisa ke Hazrat Hamza aur wahshi-bin-harab (Raziallahu anhu) hain.)"
4893,"Wakee ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne abu-Zinad se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4894,"Hammam-bin-Munabbah se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin unmein se ye hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala do shakhson ki taraf dekh kar hansta hai, unmein se aik shakhs doosrey ko qatl karta hai aur wo donon jannat mein dakhil ho jatey hain. sahaba kiram ne puchha : Allah ke rasool ! kaisey? aap ne farmaya : ye shakhs Shahid kiya jata hai aur jannat ke andar chala jata hai, phir Allah Taala doosrey (qaatil) par nazar inayat farmata hai, usey Islam ki hidayat ata karta hai, phir wo Allah ki raah mein jihad karta hai aur Shahid kar diya jata hai."
4895,Alaa ke walid ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kaafir aur usko qatl karne wala (musalman) jahannam mein kabhi ikatthey nahi hongey.
4896,"Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do log jahannam mein is tarah ikatthey nahi hongey ke ikatthey honey ki wjah se aik shakhs doosrey ko nuqsan pahuncha sakey. kaha ki : Allah ke rasool ! wo kon hain? farmaya : wo momin jisne (jihad kartey huey) kisi kaafir ko qatl kiya, phir Deen par mazbooti se jama raha."
4897,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Amr Shebani se, unhon-ne abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ontni ki mahaar (nakel) pakdey huey aaya aur kehney laga : ye Allah ki raah (jihad) mein hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhen iske badley mein qiyamat ke din saat so oontniyan milein gi aur sabhi nakel samet hongi ."
4898,Zayda aur Shoba donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
4899,"abu-Muawia ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Amr Shebani se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! mera sawari ka janwar zaaya ho gaya hai, aap mujhey sawari muhaiya kar dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere paas sawari nahi hai. aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main usko aisa shakhs batata hun jo usey sawari ka janwar muhaiya kar dega. aap ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne kisi neki ka pata bataya, uske liye (bhi) neki karne waley ke jaisa ajr hai."
4900,"Isa-bin-Yonus , Shoba aur Sufiyan sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki."
4901,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke qabila Aslam ke aik naujawaan ne aa kar kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main jihad karna chahta hun aur mere paas istitaat nahi ke iska saman baandh sakoon. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum falan shakhs ke paas chaley jao, us ne jihad ka saman taiyaar kiya tha lekin wo bimar ho gaya hai. wo naujawaan us aadmi ke paas gaya aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum ko salam kehtey hain aur farmatey hain : wo Sara saman mujhey de do jo tum ne (jihad ke liye) taiyaar kiya hai. unhon-ne kaha : aey falan bevi ! maine jo kuchh (jihad ke liye) taiyaar kiya tha usey de do aur is mein se koi cheez bacha ke na rakho, Allah ki qism ! aisey nahi hoga ke tum usmein se kuchh bacha ke rakho aur is mein se tumharey liye barkat ho."
4902,"Bukair-bin-Ashajj ne Basar-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne Allah ke rastey mein jang karne waley kisi aadmi ko samane-jihad muhaiya kiya to yaqinan usne bhi jihad kiya aur jis shakhs ne ghaazi ke ghar walon ki achi tarah dekh bhaal ki to yaqinan usne bhi jihad kiya."
4903,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Basar-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne kisi Mujahid ke liye saman muhaiya kiya to yaqinan us ne jihad kiya aur jisne Mujahid ke peechhey iske ghar walon ki dekh bhaal ki usne bhi jihad kiya."
4904,"Ali-bin-Mubarak ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Mehri ke Maula abu-Saeed ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu- Lahyaan ke khilaf aik lashkar rawaana kiya aur farmaya : har ( ghar ke) do mardon mein se aik mard uthey aur jaey, sawab mein donon Sharik hongey."
4905,"Husain ne Yahya (bin-abi-kaseer ( se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Mehri ke Maula abu-Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik lashkar bheja , usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah."
4906,Sheban ne Yahya se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
4907,"Mehri ke aazad karda ghulam Yazeed-bin-abi-Saeed ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah ne banu-Lahiyaan ki taraf aik lashkar rawaana kiya aur farmaya : har do aadmiyon mein se aik aadmi (jihad ke liye nikley) aur farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs bhi (jihad ke liye) nikalney waley ke ahal aur ayaal aur maal aur mataa (daulat) ki achi tarah dekh bhaal ke liye peechhey rahega , nikalney waley ke ajr mein se aadha usey milega. (yani jihad karne waley aur peechhey khayal rakhney waley donon ke liye sawab hai. peechhey reh kar khayal rakhney waley ko bhi ghar mein rahtey huey aadha sawab mil jaeyga.)"
4908,"Sufiyan (Sory) ne Alqama-bin-Marsad se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Barida se, unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ghar mein baithney walon ke liye mujahideen ki aurton ki izzat aur hurmat isi tarah hai jis tarah unki apni maaon ki hurmat aur izzat hai. aur gharon mein baithney walon mein se jo bhi shakhs mujaahideen ke ghar walon ki dekh bhaal ka zimme daar hai, phir unke mamley mein unke sath khayanat karta hai) poori tarah dekh bhaal nahi karta ( to usko qiyamat ke din us ( Mujahid (ke samney khada kiya jaeyga aur wo iske amal mein se jitna chaahega ley lega , ab tumhara (is saza ke barey mein) kiya khayal hai? ( kotaahi karne waley ne mujahideen ke ghar walon ki dekh bhaal mein kotahi karke nek amal bhi kiye hongey to wo us se chhin jaeinge aur ho sakta hai uske paas kuchh bhi na bachchey.)"
4909,"Misar ne hamein Alqama-bin-Marsad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne-bareeda se, unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( phir Sufiyan ( Sory ki hadis ke ham mana ( hadis bayan ki.)"
4910,Qa'anab ne Alqama-bin-Marsad se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki : aur farmaya : ( usey kaha jaeyga ke) tum uski nekiyon mein se jo chaho ley lo phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya : tum kiya samajhtey ho?
4911,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin-Bashar ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz ibne-Musanna ke hain. padhi. donon ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (bin-aazib (Raziallahu anhu)) se suna, wo Quran Majeed ki aayat : mominon mein se ghar baithney waale, jo ma'zoor nahi aur Allah ki raah mein jihad karne waley barabar nahi, ke barey mein keh rahe they ( aayat , darmyan waley hissey jo ma'zoor nahi ke baghair nazil hui ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya, wo aik shaaney ki haddi ley aaey aur is par ye aayat likh de. is mauqe par Hazrat ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne naa-beenaa honey ki shikayat ki, tab ye aayat ( darmyan ke hissey samet is tarah) utri : mominon mein se ghar baithney waale, jo ma'zoor nahi aur Allah ki raah mein jihad karne waley barabar nahi. Shoba ne kaha : mujhey aik shakhs ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se aayat : baithney waley barabar nahi Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki tarah bayan ki, ibne-Bashar ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Sad-bin-Ibrahim ne apne walid se, unhon-ne aik aadmi se, us ne Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, (pehli hadis ki sanad mukammal aur sahi hai. ye donon sanadein zabt aur taaid ke liye hain.)"
4912,"Misar ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab aayat : ''mominon mein se ghar baithney waley mujaahidon ke barabar nahi'' nazil hui to ( Abdullah ( ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu ki, tab ( غَيْرُ أُولِى ٱلضَّرَرِ ( (jo ma'zoor nahi (ke alfaz nazil huey."
4913,"Saeed-bin-Amr ash-asi aur Saeed-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki : . padhi. alfaz Saeed ke hain. padhi. kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Amr se khabar di : unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! agar main ( Allah ki raah mein ladtey huey) Shahid kar diya jaun to main kahan hoonga? farmaya : jannat mein. us shakhs ke hath mein jo khajoorein thin us ne unko phainkaa , phir lada yahan tak ke Shahid ho gaya aur Suwed ki riwayat mein ye hai : aik shakhs ne Uhud ke din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kiya."
4914,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Ansar ke aik qabeeley , banu-nabiyat mein se aik shakhs (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein) aaya aur us ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ka mustahiq nahi aur bila shubah aap Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool hain. phir aagey badha , ( khub ( jang ki yahan tak ke Shahid kar diya gaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is shakhs ne amal bahut kam kiya aur usko ajr bahut zyada ata kiya gaya."
4915,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Sufiyan ki khabar laney ke liye busaisa ( khazraji Ansari ( (Raziallahu anhu) ko jaasus bana kar bheja ke dekhey Abu-Sufiyan ke) tijarati ( qafley ki kya surate-haal hai? jis waqt wo wapas aaya to ghar mein mere aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke siwa aur koi nahi tha. padhi. (Sabit ne) kaha : mujhey ye maalum nahi ke unhon ne ye baat Ummul-Momenin ke alawaa kahi ya nahi. padhi. kaha is ne aa kar aapko saari baat batai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya : hamein kuchh ( karna ( matloob hai, so jiske paas sawari maujood ho wo hamarey sath Sawar ho kar chaley. kuchh log oopri Madina mein) maujood ( apni sawaariyan laney ki ijazat talab karne lagey. aap ne farmaya : nahi, sirf wahi log ( sath chalein ( jinki sawaariyaan yahin maujood hon. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke ashaab chal padey aur mushrekeen se pahley badr pahunch gaey, mushrekeen bhi aa pahunchey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi shakhs , jab tak main uske peechhey na hun, kisi cheez par pesh qadmii na kare. mushrekeen qareeb aagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is jannat ki taraf badh jiski chaudai aasman aur zamin hain. kaha : (ye sun kar) Hazrat Umair-bin-Hammam Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : ya Rasulullah ! jannat jiska arz aasman aur zamin hai? aap ne farmaya : haan. usne kaha : waah-waah ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne ye waah-waah kis wjah se kaha ? usne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! is ummeed ke siwa aur kisi wjah se nahi (kaha (ke main ( bhi) jannat walon mein se ho jaun , aap ne farmaya : bila shubah tum ahle-jannat mein se ho. Hazrat Umer (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne tarkash se kuchh khajoorein nikal kar khaani shuru kin, phir kehney lagey : agar main apni in khajooron ko kha leney tak zinda raha to phir ye badi lambi zindagi hogi (yani jannat milney mein der ho jaeygi) , phir unhon-ne , jo khajoorein unke paas thin, phenki aur ladai shuru kar di yahan tak ke Shahid ho gaey."
4916,"Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdullah-bin-Qais se riwayat hai, unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine apne walid se, jab wo dushman ka saamna kar rahe they, suna : wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat ke darwazey talwaaron ke saaey taley ( hotey ( hain. ye sun kar aik khasta haal shakhs khada hua aur kehney laga : abu-Musa ! kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khud ye farmatey huey suna tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan. ye sun kar wo shakhs wapas apne sathiyon ke paas gaya aur kehney laga : main tumhen salam kehta hun, phir us ne apni talwaar ki niyaam tod kar phenk di aur talwaar lekar badha , us se shamsheer zani ki yahan tak ke Shahid kar diya gaya."
4917,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kehney lagey : hamarey sath kuchh aadmi bhej dein jo ( hamein ( Quran aur sunnat ki taleem dein. aap ne unke sath sattar (70) Ansari bhej diye jinhein qir'a kaha jata tha, unmein mere maamun Hazrat haram (bin-milhaan (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi they, ye log raat ke waqt Quran padhtey they, aik doosrey ko sunatey they, Quran ki taleem hasil kartey they, aur din ko masjid mein pani la kar rakhtey they aur jangal se lakdiyan la kar farokht kartey aur us se ashabe-Suffa aur fuqaraa ke liye khana khareedtey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein un ( aaney waley kaafiron ( ki taraf bheja aur unhon-ne manzil par pahunchne se pahley ( rastey hi mein dhokey se) un par hamla kar diya aur unhein Shahid kar diya. us waqt unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ! hamari taraf se hamarey Nabi ko ye paigham pahuncha de ke hamari tujh se mulaqat ho gaee hai. ham tujh se razi ho gaey hain aur to ham se razi ho gaya hai. us saanihey (hadise) mein aik shakhs ne peechhey se aa kar Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke maamun , haram (bin-milhaan ( (Raziallahu anhu) ko is tarah neza maara ke wo aar paar ho gaya to unhon-ne kaha : rabe Kaba ki qism ! main kaamyaab ho gaya, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab se farmaya : tumharey bhai Shahid kar diye gaey hain aur unhon-ne kaha hai : aey Allah ! hamarey Nabi ko ye paigham pahuncha de ke ham ne tujh se mulaqat kar li hai, ham tujh se razi ho gaey hain aur to ham se razi ho gaya hai."
4918,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere chacha jinke naam par mera naam rakha gaya hai, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-badr mein hazir nahi ho sakey they aur ye baat un par bahut sakht guzri thi. unhon-ne kaha : ye pahlai jang thi jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sharik huey aur main us se ghair hazir raha, iske baad agar Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath koi ladaai  mujhey dikhai to Allah mujhey bhi dekhega ke main kya karta hun. wo in kalimaat ke ilawa koi aur baat kehney se darey (dil mein bahut kuchh kar guzarney ka azm tha lekin is baat se zyada kuchh nahi kaha) phir wo Uhud ki jang ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik huey, kaha : phir Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) unke samney aaey to ( mere chacha ( Anas (bin-nazar) (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : abu-Amr ! kidhar ? ( phir kaha : ( jannat ki khushbu kaisi ajeeb hai ! jo mujhey pahaad Uhud ke peechhey se aa rahi hai, phir wo kaafiron se ladey yahan tak ke Shahid ho gaey. unke jism par talwaar , neze aur teeron ke assi se uper zakhm paaey gaey. unki behan , meri phoophi , Rabe binte-nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine apne bhai (ki laash ( ko sirf unki ungliyon ke poron se pehchaana tha, (usi mauqe par) ye aayat nazil hui : ''(mominon mein se) kitney mard hain ke jis (qaul) par unhon-ne Allah se ahad kiya tha, usey sach kar dikhaya , unmein se kuchh aisey hain jinhoney apna zimma pura kar diya, aur unmein se koi aisey hain jo muntazir hain, wo zarra barabar tabdeel nahi huey (apne Allah ke sath kiye huey ahad par qaaim hain.)'' sahaba kiram ka khayal ye tha ke ye aayat Hazrat Anas (bin-nazar ( (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ke barey mein nazil hui."
4919,"Amr-bin-Murra ne kaha : maine abu-Waeil ( Shaqiq ( se suna, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke aik dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! koi shakhs maale-ghanimat ki khaatir ladtaa hai, koi shakhs isliye ladtaa hai ke us (ke kaarnaamon) ka zikr ho aur koi isliye ladtaa hai ke) ladai aur shuja'at ( mein uske maqam ko dekha jaey, unmein se Allah ke rastey mein) ladney wala ( kon hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo shakhs jo isliye ladey ke Allah ka kalima uncha ho, wahi Allah ke rastey mein (ladney wala) hai."
4920,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisey shakhs ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya jo shuja'at ke liye ladtaa hai, koi (qaumi) hamiyat ke liye ladtaa hai, koi dikhaawey ke liye ladtaa hai, unmein se Allah ki raah main ( ladney wala ( kon hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs isliye lada ke Allah ka kalima sabse uncha ho to wahi Allah ke liye ladney wala hai."
4921,"Isa-bin-Yonus ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Shaqiq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ham mein se koi shakhs izhare shuja'at ke liye ladtaa hai. phir usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4922,"Mansoor ne abu-Waeil se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Allah ki raah mein jang karne ke mutaalliq sawal kiya aur kaha : aik shakhs ghussey ki wjah se jang karta hai, aik shakhs ( qaumi ( hamiyat ki bina par jang karta hai. kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf apna sar Mubarak uthaya aur sirf isliye uthaya ke wo aadmi khada hua tha aur farmaya : jo shakhs isliye lada ke Allah ka kalima sabse uncha ho, wahi Allah ki raah main ( ladney wala ( hai."
4923,"Khalid-bin-Haaris ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Younus-bin-Yoosuf ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ( jamghatey ke baad) log Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se chhat gaey to ahale Sham mein se naatil (bin-Qais-juzaamii-raees ahale Sham (Syria) ( ne unse kaha : Shekh ! mujhey aisi hadis sunain jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho, kaha : haan , maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : qiyamat ke roz sabse pahlaa shakhs jiske khilaf faisla aayega , wo hoga jisey Shahid kar diya gaya. usey pesh kiya jaeyga Allah Taala usey apni ( ata karda ( nemat ki pehchan kiraaey ga to wo usey pehchan lega. wo poochhega tu ney is nemat ke sath kya kiya? wo kahega : maine teri raah mein ladai ki yahan tak ke mujhey Shahid kar diya gaya. ( Allah Taala ( farmaeyga tu ney jhoot bola. tum isliye ladey they ke kaha jaey : ye ( shakhs) jari (nidar) hai. aur yahi kaha gaya, phir uske barey mein hukm diya jaeyga to us aadmi ko munh ke bal ghaseetaa jaeyga yahan tak ke aag mein daal diya jaeyga aur wo aadmi jisne ilm padha , padhaayaa aur Quran ki qirat ki, usey pesh kiya jaeyga ( Allah Taala ( usey apni ne'maton ki pehchan kiraaey ga , wo pehchan kar lega , wo farmaeyga : tu ney in ne'maton ke sath kya kiya ? wo kahega : maine ilm padha aur padhaayaa aur teri khaatir Quran ki qirat ki. ( Allah ( farmaeyga : tu ney jhoot bola, tu ney isliye ilm padha ke kaha jaey (ye ( aalim hai aur tu ney Quran isliye padha ke kaha jaey : ye qaari hai, wo kaha gaya, phir uske barey mein hukm diya jaeyga, usey munh ke bal ghaseetaa jaeyga yahan tak ke aag mein daal diya jaeyga aur wo aadmi jis par Allah ne wusat ki aur har qisam ka maal ata kiya. usey laya jaeyga Allah Taala usey apni ne'maton ki pehchan kiraaey ga , wo pehchan lega. Allah farmaeyga : tum ne unmein kya kiya? kahega : maine koi raah nahi chhodi jis main tumhen pasand hai ke maal kharch kiya jaey magar har aisi raah mein kharch kiya. Allah farmaeyga : tum ne jhoot bola hai, tum ne (ye sab ( isliye kiya taake kaha jaey, wo data (sakhi) hai, aisa hi kaha gaya, phir uske barey mein hukm diya jaeyga, to usey munh ke bal ghaseetaa jaeyga, phir aag mein daal diya jaeyga."
4924,"Hujjaj-bin-Muhammad ne hamein ibne-Juraij se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Younus-bin-Yoosuf ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : log Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se chhat gaey to naatil shaami ne kaha, padhi. aur (iske baad) Khalid-bin-Haaris ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4925,"Hewa-bin-shureh ne abu-Haani se riwayat ki, unhon-ne abu-Abdur-Rehman habli se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ladney wali koi bhi jamat jo Allah ki raah mein jang karti hai, phir wo log maale-ghanimat hasil kar letey hain to wo aakhirat ke ajr se do hissey fauran hasil kar letey hain, unke liye aik baqi reh jata hai aur agar wo ghaneemat hasil nahi kartey to (aakhirat mein) unka ajr pura hoga."
4926,"Naafe-bin-Yazeed ne kaha : mujhey abu-Haani ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Abdur-Rehman-hablii ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo bhi ghaazi jamat ya lashkar jihad karey, ghaneemat hasil karey aur salamat rahe to unhon-ne apne do tehai ajr fauran (yahin) hasil kar liye aur jo bhi ghaazi jamat ya lashkar khali hath lautey aur zakhm khaaey to un logon ke ajr mukammal hongey."
4927,"Imam Malik ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama-bin-waqaas se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : amal ka daaromadar niyat par hi hai, aur aadmi ke liye wahi ( ajr ( hai jiski us ne niyat ki. jis shakhs ki hijrat Allah aur uske rasool ki taraf thi to uski hijrat Allah aur uske rasool ki taraf hai aur jis shakhs ki hijrat duniya hasil karne ke liye ya kisi aurat se nikah karne ke liye thi to uski hijrat usi cheez ki taraf hai jiski taraf us ne hijrat ki thi."
4928,"Leis, Hammad-bin-Zaid , abdul-wahaab Saqafi , Sulaiman-bin-Hayyan , Hafs-bin-Ghiyas , Yazid-bin-Harun , ibne-Mubarak aur Sufiyan sab ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, Malik ki sanad aur unki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki. Sufiyan ki hadis mein hai : maine Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko member par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis bayan kartey huey suna."
4929,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne sachey dil se shahadat talab ki, usey ata kar di jati hai) ajr ata kar diya jata hai) chahey wo usey ( amalan ( hasil na ho sakey."
4930,"abu-Taahir aur Hurmala-bin-Yahya ne mujhey hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Hurmala ke hain. padhi. abu-Taahir ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne khabar di, Hurmala ne kaha : hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Shuraih ne hadis bayan ki ke Sahal-bin-abi-Amama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef ne apne walid ke waastey se apne dada se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs sachey dil se Allah ki shahadat maangey , Allah usey shohdaa ke maraatib tak pahuncha deta hai, chahey wo apne bistar hi par kyon na faut ho. abu-Taahir ne apni hadis mein sachey (dil ( se ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
4931,"Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-saham-antaki ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne Wuhaib Makki se khabar di, unhon-ne Umar-bin-Muhammad-bin Munkadir se, unhon-ne Sumai se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs mar gaya aur jihad kiya na dil mein jihad ka irada hi kiya, wo nifaq ki aik qisam mein maraa. ibne-saham ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ka qaul hai : hamein ye samajh mein aata hai ke ye (hukm) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein tha (jab jihad ki sangeen zarurat thi. bahut badey mumaalik ke Islam mein dakhil honey aur dushmanon se maamoon ho janey ke baad ab har kisi ki jihad mein shumooliyat ki itni shadeed zarurat nahi rahi. ("
4932,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham aik ghazwey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, aap ne farmaya : Madina mein aisey log bhi hain ke tum kisi rastey par nahi chaltey ya kisi wadi ko tay nahi kartey magar wo tumharey sath hotey hain, unhein bimari ne rok rakha hai."
4933,"abu-Muawia , Wakee aur Isa-bin-Yonus sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, magar Wakee ki hadis mein (magar wo tumharey sath hotey hain ke bajaey) magar wo tumharey sath ajr mein Sharik hotey hain hai."
4934,"Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat umme-Haraam binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) (jo huzoor ki dudh-sharik khala lagti thin) ke paas tashrif ley jatey aur wo aapko khana pesh karti thin, ( baad iske ( wo Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein) aa gai) thin, aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahaan gaey, unhon-ne aapko khana pesh kiya aur phir baith kar aap ke sar mein juein talash karne lagein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey, phir aap hanstey huey bedaar huey, Hazrat umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap kyon hans rahe hain? aap ne farmaya : meri ummat ke kuchh log , Allah ki raah mein jihad kartey huey mere samney pesh kiye gaey, wo us samandar ki pusht par Sawar hongey. wo takht par baithey huey badshah hongey, ya apne apney takht par baithey huey badshahon ki tarah hongey. unhein shak tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaayaa? kaha : to umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! Allah se dua kijiye ke wo mujhey bhi un mujaahideen mein shamil kar de. aap ne unke liye dua ki aur phir apna sar ( takiye par) rakh kar so gaey, phir aap hanstey huey bedaar huey, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap kyon hans rahe hain? aap ne farmaya : mujhey ( khuwab mein) meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ki raah mein jihad kartey huey dikhaaey gaey. jis tarah pehli martaba farmaya tha, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap Allah se dua kijiye ke wo mujhey bhi unmein shamil kar de. aap ne farmaya : tum awwaleen logon mein se ho. phir Hazrat umme-Haraam-binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamaney mein samandar mein (bahri bedey par) sawar huin aur jab samandar se bahar niklin to apni sawari ke janwar se gir kar Shahid ho gain. (is tarah shahadat paai.)"
4935,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa-bin-hibbaan se, unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala thin, kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey yahaan tashrif laey aur hamarey yahaan qailula farmaya, phir aap hanstey huey bedaar huey. maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap par mere maan-baap qurbaan ! aap ke hansney ka sabab kya hai? aap ne farmaya : mujhey meri ummat ka aik giroh dikhaya gaya jo samandar ki peeth par Sawar hain, jaisey badshah apne-apne takht par baithey hon. maine kaha : aap Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unmein shamil kar de. aap ne farmaya : tum unhi mein ho. Hazrat umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap phir so gaey aur aap dobara jaagey to bhi aap hans rahe they. maine (phir) aap se sawal kiya to aap ne isi tarah farmaya, maine kaha : aap Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke wo mujhey bhi unmein shamil kar de. aap ne farmaya : tum awwaleen logon mein se ho. kaha : phir iske baad Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse nikah kar liya. unhon-ne samandar ke rastey jihad kiya aur Hazrat umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne sath le gaey, jab wo pahunchin to unke paas aik khachchar laai gaee, wo is par Sawar huin lekin us ne unko gira diya jis se unki gardan toot gaee. (aur is tarah unhon-ne shahadat paai.)"
4936,"Leis ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne ibne-hibbaan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne apni khala umme-Haraam-binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere qareeb hi so gaey, phir aap muskuratey huey bedaar huey, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap kis baat par hans rahe hain? aap ne farmaya : mujhey meri ummat ke kuchh log dikhaaey gaey jo us bahare-akhzar par Sawar ho kar ja rahe hain. phir Hammad-bin-Zaid ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
4937,"Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki khala , binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif laey aur unke yahaan (takiye par) sar rakh kar so gaey, iske baad Ishaq-bin-abi-Talha aur Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa-bin-hibbaan ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
4938,"Lais-bin-Sad ne hamein Ayub-bin-Musa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mak-hool se, unhon-ne Shurehbeel-bin-Simt se, unhon-ne Salman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : aik din aur aik raat sarhad par pahra denaa, aik maah ke rozon aur qiyam se behtar hai aur agar (pahra dene wala) faut ho gaya to uska wo amal jo wo kar raha tha, (aainda bhi) jari rahega , uske liye uska rizq jari kiya jaeyga aur wo (qabr mein sawalat karke) imtihaan leney waley se mehfooz rahega."
4939,"abu-Ubaida-bin-Aqba ne Shurehbeel-bin-Simt se, unhon-ne Salman-khair (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Ayub-bin-Musa se Leis ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki."
4940,"sumi ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik baar aik shakhs kisi rastey par ja raha tha, us ne rastey mein aik khaardaar shaakh dekhi to usko (rastey se) peechhey kar diya, Allah Taala ne usey uske amal ki jazaa di aur usko bakhsh diya. phir aap ne farmaya : Shahid panch ( qism ke ashkhaas ( hain : (1) taaoon ki bimari mein marney wala. (2) pet ki bimari mein marney wala. (3) doob kar marney wala. (4) kisi cheez ke nichey dab kar marney wala. (5) aur jo shakhs izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki raah mein (ladtey huey) Shahid hua."
4941,"Jarir ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum aapas mein (baat kartey huey) Shahid kis ko shumaar kartey ho? sahaba ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein qatl kiya jaey wo Shahid hai. aap ne farmaya : phir to meri ummat ke shohdaa bahut kam huey. sahaba ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! phir wo kon hain? aap ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein maara jaey wo Shahid hai aur jo shakhs Allah ki raah main (talabe-ilm, safar Haj , jihad ke doran main apni maut ( mar jaey wo Shahid hai, jo shakhs taaoon mein marey wo Shahid hai, jo shakhs pet ki bimari main (mubtala ho kar) mar jaey wo Shahid hai. ( Abu-Saleh se bayan karne waley aik aur rawi Ubaidullah ( bin-muqsim ne (Suhail-bin-abi Saleh se) kaha : main tumharey walid ke barey mein gawahi deta hun ke unhon-ne ( hadis bayan kartey huey ye bhi) kaha tha : aur gharq honey wala Shahid hai."
4942,"Khalid ne hamein Suhel se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unki hadis mein hai : Suhel ne kaha : Ubaidullah-bin-muqsim ne ( Suhel se) kaha ke main tumharey bhai ke barey mein (bhi) gawahi deta hun ke us hadis (ko apne walid se bayan kartey huey us ( mein ye izafa kiya tha : aur jo gharq ho jaey wo Shahid hai."
4943,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Suhel ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, unki hadis mein hai, kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-muqsim ne Abu-Saleh se khabar di, aur is mein izafa kiya : gharq honey wala Shahid hai."
4944,"abdul-Wahid-bin-Ziyad ne kaha : hamein Aasim ne Hafsa-binte-Sirin se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se puchha : Yahya-bin-abi-Umra kis bimari se faut huey they? unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : taaoon se. unhon-ne kaha : to unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : taaoon (se maut) har musalman ke liye shahadat hai."
4945,Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Aasim se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4946,"samaama-bin-shufee se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap member par farma rahe they : tum unke muqaabley ke liye jitni kar sako, quwwat taiyaar karo.sun rakho ! quwwat teer andazi (ka naam ( hai, sun rakho ! quwwat teer andazi (ka naam) hai, sun rakho ! quwwat teer andazi (ka naam) hai."
4947,"ibne- Wahab ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Haris ne abu-Ali ( samaama-bin-shafi) se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jald hi tumharey liye bahut si zaminon (par qabzey) ke darwazey khol diye jaeinge aur Allah tumharey liye kafi hoga, isliye tum mein se koi apne teeron ki mashq se ghaafil na rahe."
4948,Main saiyedna Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mazkura (uper zikr) hadis ki manind (tarah) riwayat naql kartey hain.
4949,"Haaris-bin-Yaqoob ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-shumaasa se riwayat ki ke fuqaim lakhmi ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap ( teer chhodney aur ja lagney ke) un do nishaanon ke darmyan chakkar lagaatey hain jabke aap boodhey hain aur ye aap ke liye baaise mashaqqat bhi hai. Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik baat na suni hoti to main ye takleef na uthata . Haris ne kaha : maine ibne-Shumaasa se puchha : wo baat kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jis shakhs ne teer andazi seekhi, phir usko tark kar diya, wo ham mein se nahi hai. ya (farmaya:) us ne nafarmani ki."
4950,Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hamesha meri ummat ka aik giroh haq par qaaim rahega koi unko nuqsan na pahuncha sakega yahan tak ke Allah Taala ka hukm aawey (yani qiyamat (aur wo isi haal mein hongey.
4951,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra . (is hadis ka bayan kitabul-Imaan mein guzra hai.)
4952,tarjama wahi jo uper guzra .
4953,Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye Deen barabar qaaim rahega aur iske uper ladti rahegi aik jamat ( kaafiron se aur mukhaalifon se) musalmanon ki qiyamat honey tak.
4954,Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai maine suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap farmatey they hamesha aik giroh meri ummat ka haq par ladtaa rahega qiyamat tak.
4955,"Umair-bin-Hani se riwayat hai maine Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se suna member par, wo kehtey they maine suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap farmatey they hamesha aik giroh meri ummat ka Allah ke hukm par qaaim rahega jo koi unko bigaadnaa chahey wo kuchh bigaad na sakega. yahan tak ke Allah ka hukm aan pahunchey aur wo ghalib raheingey logon par."
4956,Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ki Allah Taala bhalai chahta hai usko Deen mein samajh deta hai aur hamesha aik jamat musalmanon ki haq par ladti rahegi aur ghalib rahegi un par jo unse ladein qiyamat tak.
4957,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-shumaasa Mehri se riwayat hai main muslima-bin-mukhlid ke paas betha tha unke paas Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) they. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha qiyamat qaaim na hogi magar badtareen makhlooq par, wo badtar hongey jahiliyat walon se ,Allah taala se jis baat ki dua karengey Allah Taala unko raddh kar de ga. log isi haal mein they ke Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) aaey Muslima ne unse kaha aey Aqba ! Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kya kehtey hain? Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha wo mujh se zyada jantey hain par maine to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey they hamesha meri ummat ka aik giroh ya aik jamat Allah ke hukm par ladti rahegi aur apne dushman par ghalib rahegi jo koi unka khilaf khada hoga unko kuchh nuqsan na pahuncha sakega yahan tak ke qiyamat aa jaawey gi. aur wo usi haal mein hongey. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha be-shak (hazrat ne aisa farmaya) lekin phir Allah aik hawa bhejeyga jis mein mushk ki si boo hogi aur resham ki tarah badan par lagey gi wo na chhodegi , kisi shakhs ko jiske dil mein aik daney barabar bhi imaan hoga. balke usko maarey jaawey gi. baad iske sab burey kaafir log reh jaawen gey unhi par qiyamat qaaim hogi."
4958,Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hamesha maghrib waley haq par ghalib raheingey yahan tak ke qiyamat qaaim hogi.
4959,"Jarir ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum shadabi (hariyali) (ke zamaney) mein safar karo to zamin mein se oonton ko unka hissey do aur jab tum khushk saali (ya qahat zada zameen) mein safar karo to us zamin par se jaldi guzro aur jab tum raat ke aakhiri hissey mein manzil karo to guzar gaah se hat jao kyonke raat ko wo ( rastey ki) jagah kidon-makaudo ka thikana hoti hai. ( wahan apni khuraak ke husool ke liye aatey hain.)"
4960,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum shadabi (ke zamaney) mein safar karo to zamin se oonton ko unka hissey do aur jab tum khushk saali mein safar karo to us (se mutaassira ilaaqey mein) se un (oonton ki taangon) ka goodaa bacha kar ley jao ( tez raftaarii se nikal jao taake zyada arsa bhookey reh kar wo kamzor na ho jayen) aur jab tum raat ke aakhiri hissey mein qiyam karo to guzargaah mein thaharney se ijtinab karo kyonke raat ke waqt wo jagah janwaron ki guzar gaah aur kidey-makaude ki aamaajgaah hoti hai."
4961,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi ne kaha : maine Imam Malik se puchha : Sumai ne aapko Abu-Saleh ke waastey se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : safar azab ka aik tukda hai, wo tum mein se aik ( musaafir ( ko soney , khaney aur peeney se rok deta hai, jab tum mein se koi shakhs wo kaam sar anjam de chukey jo uske peshe-nazar tha to wo jald apne ghar aaey? unhon (Imam Malik ( ne kaha : haan."
4962,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne Hammam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko apne ghar walon par dastak na detey they. aap (safar se ghar walon ke paas ( subah ko ya Sham ko tashrif latey they."
4963,"Abdus-Samad-bin-Abdul-Waris ne kaha : hamein Hammam ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ishaq-in-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : ( gharon mein) dakhil na hotey they."
4964,"Hushaim ne Sayyar se, unhon-ne ( Aamir ( Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham aik ghazwey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, jab ham Madina pahunchey to ham gharon ke andar dakhil honey ke liye janey lagey to aap ne farmaya : ruk jao, yahan tak ke ham ( kuchh taakheer se) raat ke waqt , yani isha ke waqt jayen taake bikhrey baalon wali apne baal sanwaar ley aur shauhar ki ghair maujoodgi mein rehney wali apni safaaii kare."
4965,"Abdus-Samad ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Sayyar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aamir (Shabi) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs raat ke waqt ghar wapas aaey to raat ko (achanak) apne ghar mein dakhil na ho (balke itni der twaqquf karey) ke shauhar ki ghair haziri mein rehney wali apni safaai kar ley aur uljhey baalon wali baal sanwaar ley."
4966,"Rauh-bin-Ubada ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sayyar ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4967,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Aasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab koi insan lamba waqt ghar se door raha ho to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey raat ko achcha ghar mein dakhil honey se mana farmaya."
4968,Rooh ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
4969,"Wakee ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Maharib se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke insan raat ko) achcha ( ghar walon ke paas ja pahunchey aur unko khayanat (jis tarah khawind ne kaha hua hai, is tarah na rehney (ka mujrim samjhey aur unki kamzoriyaan dhoondey."
4970,Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : Sufiyan ne kaha : mujhey malum nahi ke unko khayanat ka murtakib samjhey aur unki kamzoriyaan talash karey ke alfaz hadis mein hain ya nahi.
4971,"hamein Shoba ne Maharib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( achcha (raat ko ghar aaney ki karaahat bayan ki aur ye jumla bayan nahi kiya : unko  khayanat karne wala samjhey aur unki kamzoriyaan talash kare."
